id-131176112%2Cimgsize-63838.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fann-robinson-stuntwoman-and-cult-sci-fi-legend-dies-at-96-death-revealed-eight-months-later%2Farticleshow%2F131175949.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131175949.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20world%20has%20lost%20a%20true%20icon%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20Ann%20Robinson%20at%2096%2C%20the%20veteran%20actress%20and%20renowned%20stuntwoman%20who%20captivated%20audiences%20as%20Sylvia%20in%20the%201953%20classic%20'The%20War%20Of%20The%20Worlds.'%20Robinson's%20legacy%20continued%20with%20her%20return%20in%20Spielberg's%202005%20version%2C%20and%20she%20slipped%20away%20peacefully%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lowe's%20is%20betting%20on%20MrBeast%20to%20drive%20'lipstick%20effect'%20sales%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mrbeast%20Lowe's%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06de30abc4e9d88574a510%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224098%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMrBeast%20and%20Lowe's%20are%20teaming%20up.%3Cp%3ELowe's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELowe's%20is%20partnering%20with%20MrBeast%20on%20a%20range%20of%20toys%20and%20in-store%20kids%20workshops.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELowe's%20CMO%20Jen%20Wilson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20retailer%20expects%20the%20toys%20and%20workshops%20to%20sell%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20home%20improvement%20retailer%20wants%20to%20boost%20the%20appeal%20of%20its%20brand%20among%20younger%20audiences.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20wants%20to%20inspire%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20consumers%2C%20Gen%20Alpha%2C%20to%20become%20DIY%20enthusiasts.%20Enter%20MrBeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20improvement%20retailer%20said%20Monday%20it's%20rolling%20out%20MrBeast-themed%20kids%20workshops%20in%20its%20stores%20starting%20May%2030.%20Children%20will%20receive%20MrBeast%20badges%20for%20each%20workshop%20they%20complete.%20Lowe's%20is%20also%20releasing%20a%20series%20of%20buildable%20MrBeast%20toy%20kits%2C%20tied%20to%20his%20Swarms%20collectibles%20brand.%20MrBeast%20will%20earn%20royalties%20from%20the%20toy%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20CMO%20Jen%20Wilson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20company%20aims%20to%20sell%20out%20of%20both%20workshop%20places%20and%20the%20%2414.98%20(plus%20tax)%20toys.%20It's%20also%20looking%20to%20increase%20registrations%20on%20the%20Lowe's%20app%20and%20encourage%20children%20and%20their%20parents%20to%20shop%20for%20extra%20items%20while%20they're%20in-store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20not%20selling%20out%20or%20selling%20through%2C%20then%20we've%20missed%20the%20mark%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome-improvement%20retailers%20are%20navigating%20a%20challenging%20period%20as%20high%20interest%20rates%20hamper%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-market-summer-buyers-mortgate-rates-iran-war-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20housing%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20some%20consumers%20put%20off%20big%20renovation%20projects.%20Lowe's%20reported%20a%201.3%25%20rise%20in%20same-store%20sales%20in%20its%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20which%20it%20said%20was%20driven%20by%20growth%20in%20its%20Pro%2C%20online%2C%20and%20home%20services%20businesses.%20The%20company%20is%20set%20to%20report%20its%20first-quarter%20earnings%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20has%20been%20placing%20bets%20on%20what%20it%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bviral%20and%20trending%26quot%3B%20product%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20mini%20tool%20boxes%2C%20teeny%20totes%2C%20spring%20candles%2C%20and%20now%20MrBeast%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20sort%20of%20the%20lipstick%20effect%20of%20home%20improvement%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BGive%20me%20a%20small%2C%20impulsive%20item%20that%20I%20can%20buy%20that%20makes%20me%20feel%20good%2C%20that%20brings%20me%20joy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lipstick%20effect%20is%20a%20theory%20that%20sales%20of%20affordable%20luxuries%2C%20such%20as%20lipsticks%2C%20rise%20during%20economic%20crises%20as%20people%20seek%20smaller%20purchases%20to%20give%20them%20a%20lift%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20is%20also%20actively%20seeking%20to%20grow%20its%20relationships%20with%20younger%20generations%20living%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20its%20millennial%20target%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGen%20Alpha%20actually%20has%20a%20larger%20influence%20on%20where%20their%20parents%20shop%20and%20what%20they%20purchase%20than%20any%20other%20influence%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJimmy%20Donaldson%3C%2Fa%3E%20(aka%20MrBeast)%20is%20the%20world's%20most-popular%20YouTuber%2C%20with%20more%20than%20480%20million%20subscribers%20to%20his%20main%20channel.%20His%20Beast%20Industries%20business%20empire%20spans%20the%20candy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-says-cheaper-to-make-feastables-abroad-trump-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20brands%20Feastables%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Lunchly%2C%20MrBeast%20Lab%20action%20figures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdarren-margolias-executive-director-mrbeast-beast-philanthropy-youtube-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ephilanthropic%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20Amazon%20Prime%20show%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-reorders-beast-games-showing-grasp-creators-have-on-hollywood-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBeast%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20first%20partnered%20with%20MrBeast%20last%20year%20to%20launch%20its%20creator%20network.%20Creators%20can%20earn%20commissions%20by%20curating%20product%20selections%20on%20Lowe's%20website%20storefronts.%20Lowe's%20also%20provided%20materials%20for%20building%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-reveals-14m-city-for-beast-games-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeastCity%20complex%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0featured%20in%20%26quot%3BBeast%20Games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeil%20Saunders%2C%20a%20retail%20analyst%20at%20the%20analytics%20and%20consulting%20firm%20GlobalData%2C%20said%20Lowe's%20strategy%20to%20increase%20brand%20visibility%20among%20a%20younger%20age%20group%20with%20the%20MrBeast%20partnership%20is%20a%20smart%20move%20because%20its%20bigger%20rival%2C%20Home%20Depot%2C%20is%20usually%20top%20of%20mind%20when%20consumers%20think%20about%20home%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20thing%20the%20partnership%20does%20is%20get%20more%20young%20people%20interested%20and%20confident%20in%20home%20improvement%20tasks%2C%20which%20is%20something%20many%20struggle%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Saunders%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sort%20of%20way%20of%20seeding%20demand%20for%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-partners-lowes-for-swarms-toys-kids-workshops-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779105601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06de0cecd7cc1332baff93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-partners-lowes-for-swarms-toys-kids-workshops-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2