0technology%20in%20the%20restaurants%2C%20remodeling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20also%20elevating%20our%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Burger%20King%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20Joel%20Yashinsky%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYashinsky%20said%20the%20company%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20make%20customers%20feel%20more%20connected%20to%20the%20brand%20by%20leaning%20into%20Burger%20King's%20long-standing%20emphasis%20on%20customization%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20its%20%26quot%3BHave%20It%20Your%20Way%26quot%3B%20slogan%20introduced%20in%201974.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20guest%20to%20have%20ownership%20in%20the%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20Yashinsky%20said.%20%26quot%3BBurger%20King%20was%20the%20first%20to%20really%20realize%20people%20liked%20customization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225dcca88f-2d72-446c-84e4-96c886d599ad%5C%22%3EBurger%20King%20has%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20Whopper%2C%20betting%20big%20on%20its%20signature%20burger%20to%20fuel%20the%20chain's%20comeback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22burger%20king%20whopper%20with%20cheese%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e294d9367066d7c296e2be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBurger%20King%20recently%20updated%20its%20Whopper%20with%20a%20new%20box%2C%20bun%2C%20and%20mayonnaise.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20renewed%20focus%20includes%20recent%20campaigns%20to%20improve%20the%20Whopper's%20presentation%20and%20listening%20to%20customer%20feedback%20on%20how%20to%20elevate%20it%2C%20rather%20than%20solely%20introducing%20new%20menu%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20an%20interesting%20way%20to%20do%20it%20through%20listening%20and%20taking%20action%2C%20and%20consumers%20see%20us%20listening%20to%20the%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20Curtis%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Burger%20King%20had%20been%20receiving%20feedback%20that%20Whoppers%20often%20ended%20up%20smushed%20in%20the%20bag%20because%20they%20were%20wrapped%20only%20in%20paper.%20As%20of%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-burger-king-new-updated-whopper-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Whopper%20is%20now%20served%20in%20a%20cardboard%20box%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20chain%20also%20upgraded%20some%20of%20its%20components%2C%20adding%20a%20creamier%20mayonnaise%20and%20a%20new%2C%20glossier%20bun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20putting%20the%20guest%20first%20and%20delivering%20what%20they're%20looking%20for%20from%20Burger%20King%2C%26quot%3B%20Yashinsky%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20want%20to%20be%20a%20brand%20that%20really%20authentically%20listens%20and%20acts%20to%20what%20the%20guests%20are%20looking%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYashinsky%20said%20the%20company%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-burger-king-changing-whopper-recipe-premiumization-fast-food-value-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimprove%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20raising%20prices%20for%20customers.%20Burger%20King%20kept%20the%20Whopper%20at%20the%20same%20price%20even%20as%20it%20upgraded%20the%20burger%20and%20its%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20we're%20investing%20and%20not%20shrinking%20value%20through%20cutting%20sizes%20or%20cutting%20cost%20in%20different%20ways%2C%20but%20actually%20investing%20in%20the%20packaging%20and%20investing%20in%20a%20better%20bun%2C%20those%20little%20things%20matter%2C%20and%20customers%20notice%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220df42424-9154-4bf6-9100-9dd89ac9d355%5C%22%3EDespite%20a%20challenging%20market%2C%20the%20comeback%20is%20showing%20positive%20signs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reality%20star%20Kyle%20Cooke%20promoted%20%26quot%3BWednesdays%20should%20be%20fun%26quot%3B%20to%20support%20Whopper%20Wednesday%20on%20April%2015%2C%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a061301ecd7cc1332bafcba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223581%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReality%20star%20Kyle%20Cooke%20promoted%20%26quot%3BWednesdays%20should%20be%20fun%26quot%3B%20to%20support%20Whopper%20Wednesday%20on%20April%2015%2C%202026%3Cp%3ERoy%20Rochlin%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Burger%20King%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECurtis%20described%20Burger%20King's%20position%20several%20years%20ago%20as%20dire%2C%20saying%20the%20brand%20faced%20an%20%26quot%3Bexistential%20threat.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20when%20he%20joined%20Burger%20King%20in%202021%2C%20a%20former%20boss%20showed%20him%20an%20article%20predicting%20the%20chain%20would%20disappear%20within%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20four%20years%20after%20launching%20%26quot%3BReclaim%20the%20Flame%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20turnaround%20plan%20is%20taking%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%2C%20like%20others%20in%20the%20QSR%20industry%2C%20has%20focused%20much%20of%20its%20marketing%20on%20value%2C%20with%20campaigns%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BWhopper%20Wednesday%2C%26quot%3B%20%245%20Duos%2C%20and%20%247%20Trios%20to%20draw%20in%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20Burger%20King%20reported%205.8%25%20same-store%20sales%20growth%20in%20the%20US%2C%20outperforming%20its%20competitors%20in%20the%20QSR%20burger%20segment.%20(McDonald's%20same-store%20sales%20increased%203.9%25%2C%20while%20Wendy's%20sales%20declined%20by%207.8%25%20in%20Q1.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20notable%20increase%20from%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20when%20the%20chain%20reported%20a%201.6%25%20same-store%20sales%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20leadership%20cited%20new%2C%20family-focused%20initiatives%2C%20like%20the%20chain's%20King%20Junior%20meals%20and%20its%20SpongeBob-themed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-new-mandalorian-star-wars-menu-ranked-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeal%20collaboration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20growth.%20Curtis%20said%20in%20the%20earnings%20call%20that%20kids'%20meal%20sales%20had%20risen%20about%2040%25%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2026%2F05%2F08%2Fburger-king-president-fixed-whopper-phone-calls-from-customers.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhopper%20sales%20are%20also%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qsrmagazine.com%2Fstory%2Fburger-king-sees-u-s-sales-surge-as-reclaim-the-flame-strategy-takes-hold%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQSR%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%2C%20in%20the%20last%20quarter%2C%20Burger%20King%20restaurants%20posted%20their%20highest%20average%20Whopper%20sales%20per%20location%20in%20more%20than%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Yashinsky%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Burger%20King%20plans%20to%20continue%20modernizing%20restaurants%2C%20expanding%20its%20franchisee%20network%2C%20launching%20new%20innovations%2C%20and%20elevating%20its%20most%20popular%20menu%20items%20while%20staying%20true%20to%20the%20chain's%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBurger%20King%20will%20feel%20different%20%5Bin%20five%20years%5D%20than%20it%20does%20today%20pretty%20significantly%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20changing%20who%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20back%20more%20toward%20'Have%20It%20Your%20Way.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-comeback-plan-to-become-best-burger-chain-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779104101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06