e%20Court%20had%20vacated%20high%20court's%20stay%20on%20implementation%20of%20the%20new%20OBC%20list%20that%20had%20a%20total%20of%20140%20sub-groups%20under%20OBC-A%20and%20OBC-B%20categories%2C%20including%2080%20belonging%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20airlines%20could%20follow%20Spirit%20into%20bankruptcy%20due%20to%20the%20Iran%20war%20fuel%20crisis%2C%20Ryanair%20exec%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spirit%20Airlines%20planes%20sit%20parked%20at%20the%20Phoenix%20Goodyear%20Airport%20on%20May%208%2C%202026%20in%20Goodyear%2C%20Arizona.%20The%20budget%20airline%20ceased%20all%20operations%20on%20May%202%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0ae991ecd7cc1332bb09d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223595%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpirit%20Airlines%20ceased%20operations%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20citing%20increasing%20fuel%20prices.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Noble%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERyanair's%20CFO%20warned%20that%20more%20airlines%20could%20go%20bankrupt%20due%20to%20rising%20fuel%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20told%20CNBC%20the%20airline%20has%20plans%20for%20an%20%26quot%3BArmageddon%20situation%26quot%3B%20but%20doesn't%20expect%20that%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESpirit%20Airlines%20ceased%20operations%20earlier%20in%20May%20citing%20rising%20fuel%20costs%20as%20a%20major%20issue.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESurging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-airlines-pay-fuel-planes-fares-impact-oil-iran-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejet%20fuel%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20mean%20some%20airlines%20going%20out%20of%20business%2C%20according%20to%20the%20chief%20financial%20officer%20of%20Ryanair%2C%20Europe's%20biggest%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20will%20see%20some%20of%20the%20weaker%20carriers%20who%20were%20already%20struggling%20before%20the%20war%20possibly%20go%20to%20the%20wall%20in%20the%20winter%2C%26quot%3B%20Neil%20Sorahan%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Iran%20war%20began%20in%20late%20February%2C%20Brent%20crude%20oil%20has%20risen%20over%2050%25%20to%20more%20than%20%24110%20a%20barrel.%20Jet%20fuel%20prices%20rose%20to%20almost%20%24200%20a%20barrel%2C%20but%20have%20since%20pared%20back%20to%20about%20%24163%2C%20according%20to%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJet%20fuel%20is%20typically%20an%20airline's%20second-biggest%20expenditure%2C%20after%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-collapses-shuts-down-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpirit%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20casualty%20of%20spiking%20jet%20fuel%20prices%20so%20far.%20The%20budget%20airline%20had%20already%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20restructuring%20last%20August%2C%20but%20ceased%20operations%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20citing%20rising%20fuel%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20like%20many%20European%20airlines%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-ceo-warns-25-percent-jet-fuel-threatened-iran-war-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyanair%20has%20hedged%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20fuel%20costs%20using%20financial%20derivatives.%2080%25%20of%20its%20fuel%20is%20hedged%20at%20%2467%20per%20barrel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ryanair-pr-marketing-strategy-michael-oleary-history-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Michael%20O'Leary%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20a%20Monday%20earnings%20call.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20expect%20to%20be%20cutting%20flights%20or%20schedules%20because%20of%20higher%20oil%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESorahan%20told%20CNBC%20that%20Ryanair%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20had%20some%20concern%20around%20oil%20supply%26quot%3B%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20but%20the%20airline%20is%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20confident%26quot%3B%20there%20won't%20be%20issues%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CFO%20added%20that%20Europe%20is%20less%20dependent%20on%20oil%20imports%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20with%20more%20oil%20now%20coming%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Venezuela%2C%20and%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20said%2C%20I%20think%20prices%20will%20remain%20higher%20for%20longer%2C%20which%20puts%20Ryanair%20in%20a%20particularly%20strong%20position%2C%20given%20our%20strong%20fuel%20hedging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20budget%20airline%2C%20Ryanair%20is%20particularly%20cautious%20about%20fuel%20prices%20because%20it%20wants%20to%20keep%20ticket%20prices%20as%20low%20as%20possible%2C%20hence%20its%20strong%20hedging%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20the%20Irish%20carrier%20is%20still%20preparing%20for%20all%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20we%20have%20plans%20for%20some%20kind%20of%20Armageddon%20situation%3F%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20do%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20that%20coming%20to%20pass%2C%26quot%3B%20Sorahan%20told%20CNBC.%20%26quot%3BAs%20things%20stand%2C%20we're%20operating%20a%20full%20schedule%20this%20summer%2C%20and%20plan%20to%20operate%20a%20full%20schedule%20into%20the%20winter%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Ryanair%20reported%20that%20it%20carried%20208%20million%20passengers%20through%20the%202026%20financial%20year%2C%20consolidating%20its%20position%20as%20Europe's%20busiest%20carrier.%20Profits%20after%20tax%20also%20rose%2040%25%20to%202.26%20billion%20euros%20(%242.6%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-cfo-more-airlines-bankrupt-fuel-crisis-spirit-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779103221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0ae9c194eb4c909fb2d665%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-cfo-more-airlines-bankrupt-fuel-crisis-spirit-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20will%20see%20some%20of%20the%20weaker%20carriers%20who%20were%20already%20struggling%20before%20the%20war%20possibly%20go%20to%20the%20wall%20in%20the%20winter%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryanair's%20CFO%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIRR%20issues%20advice%20to%20New%20York%20commuters%20as%20rail%20strike%20enters%20its%203rd%20day%3A%20Work%20from%20home%20if%20you%20can%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226527%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Long%20Island%20Railroad%20train%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0ae3d994eb4c909fb2d65e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224351%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMore%20than%203%2C000%20Long%20Island%20Railroad%20workers%20are%20striking%20over%20pay%20and%20working%20conditions.%3Cp%3EAdam%20Gray%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20major%20strike%20on%20the%20Long%20Island%20Railroad%20is%20causing%20commuter%20chaos%20for%20New%20Yorkers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20LIRR%20is%20telling%20commuters%20to%20work%20from%20home%20as%20the%20strike%20rolls%20into%20the%20working%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strike%20comes%20as%20many%20New%20Yorkers%20gear%20up%20to%20head%20to%20the%20Hamptons%20for%20Memorial%20Day%20weekend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECommuters%20in%20New%20York%20are%20starting%20the%20week%20facing%20travel%20chaos%20as%20a%20strike%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flirr-grand-central-train-11-billion-nyc-abundance-agenda-infrastructure-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELong%20Island%20Railroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20enters%20its%20third%20day%2C%20and%20its%20first%20during%20the%20working%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%203%2C500%20workers%20on%20the%20train%20service%20%E2%80%94%20which%20connects%20around%208%20million%20people%20living%20on%20Long%20Island%20with%20Manhattan%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-new-york-city-miami-back-got-too-expensive-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20started%20striking%20just%20after%20midnight%20on%20Friday%20amid%20a%20dispute%20over%20pay%20and%20working%20conditions.%20The%20LIRR%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mta.info%2Farticle%2Flirr-strike-may-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserves%3C%2Fa%3E%20roughly%20300%2C000%20passengers%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLIRR%20service%20remains%20suspended%20due%20to%20the%20strike.%20Please%20work%20from%20home%20if%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20railroad's%20official%20X%20account%20posted%20at%20around%205%20a.m.%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-transport-ticket-prices-sky-high-new-york-boston-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20shared%20a%20number%20of%20alternative%20travel%20arrangements%20for%20commuters%20impacted%20by%20the%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20city-run%20shuttle%20buses%20from%20Long%20Island%20into%20the%20city%2C%20which%20began%20at%204%3A30%20a.m.%20Monday%2C%20as%20well%20as%20more%20frequent%20services%20on%20Nassau%20County%20buses%2C%20and%20the%20opening%20of%20parking%20lots%20at%20Citi%20Field%2C%20the%20home%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Mets%2C%20for%20commuters%20to%20park%20and%20take%20the%20subway%20into%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20that%20the%20railroad%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20Long%20Island%2C%26quot%3B%20Hochul%20said%20in%20a%20Sunday%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20it%2C%20life%20as%20we%20know%20it%20is%20simply%20not%20possible.%20The%20bottom%20line%20is%2C%20no%20one%20wins%20in%20a%20strike.%20Everyone%20is%20hurt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223555%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Striking%20workers%20on%20the%20Long%20Island%20Railroad%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0aec5cabc4e9d88574af09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELIRR%20workers%20picketed%20outside%20major%20New%20York%20stations%20over%20the%20weekend.%3Cp%3ELIRR%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%2C%20the%20first%20on%20the%20LIRR%20since%201994%2C%20comes%20as%20unions%20representing%20workers%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20pay%20deal%20with%20New%20York's%20Metropolitan%20Transportation%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20result%20we%20were%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MTA's%20CEO%2C%20Janno%20Lieber%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20soon%20after%20the%20strike%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20Governor%20Hochul%20said%2C%20everybody%20loses%20in%20a%20strike%20%E2%80%94%20the%20MTA%2C%20the%20thousands%20of%20workers%20who%20are%20going%20to%20lose%20wages%2C%20and%20most%20of%20all%2C%20the%20riders%20who%20rely%20on%20the%20railroad%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieber%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20responsibly%20make%20a%20deal%20that%20implodes%20MTA's%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%20come%20as%20New%20Yorkers%20gear%20up%20to%20escape%20the%20city%20for%20the%20Memorial%20Day%20weekend%2C%20with%20many%20depending%20on%20the%20LIRR%20to%20whisk%20them%20away%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhamptons-rush-staffing-summer-homes-nannies-chefs-estate-managers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Hamptons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20popular%20vacation%20destination%20around%2070%20miles%20from%20the%20city%20at%20the%20eastern%20end%20of%20Long%20Island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalks%20are%20set%20to%20resume%20between%20unions%20and%20the%20MTA%20on%20Monday%20after%20the%20National%20Mediation%20Board%20stepped%20in%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlade%2C%20the%20helicopter%20charter%20company%2C%20seized%20the%20moment%20to%20run%20an%20ad%20for%20its%20services%20on%20X%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBLADE%20commuter%20seats%20are%20now%20just%20%2495%2C%26quot%3B%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Rob%20Wiesenthal%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20prices%20are%20valid%20until%20the%20LIRR%20strike%20ends.%20A%20same-day%20ticket%20booked%20on%20Blade%20without%20the%20promotional%20pricing%20costs%20%24210.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20LIRR%20is%20on%20strike.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20are%20not.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBLADE%20Commuter%20Seats%20are%20now%20just%20%2495.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPark%20and%20fly%20with%20BLADE%20and%20commute%20between%20Long%20Island%20and%20the%20city%20in%20just%205%20minutes.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EValid%20today%20until%20the%20strike%20ends.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBook%20your%20seat%20now%20using%20code%3A%20FLYIN5%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FnYkZUN7MbH%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FnYkZUN7MbH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rob%20Wiesenthal%20(%40wiesenthal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwiesenthal%2Fstatus%2F2055845080565506333%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2017%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20LIRR's%20strikes%2C%20transportation%20workers%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flondon-underground-better-than-nyc-subway-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELondon%20Underground%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20set%20to%20walk%20out%20over%20pay%20and%20working%20conditions.%20Two%2024-hour%20strikes%20are%20planned%20in%20the%20British%20capital%20for%20Tuesday%20and%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-island-railroad-lirr-strikes-advice-commuter-chaos-new-york-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779103052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0ae44d94eb4c909fb2d660%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-island-railroad-lirr-strikes-advice-commuter-chaos-new-york-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20strike%2C%20which%20began%20soon%20after%20midnight%20on%20Friday%2C%20is%20set%20to%20cause%20chaos%20for%20commuters%20heading%20to%20New%20York%20City%20for%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Will%20Martin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'On%20important%20visit'%3A%20BJP%20justifies%20PM's%20foreign%20tour%20after%20oppn's%20'where's%20Modi'%20question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779103033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131174755%2Cimgsize-574016.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fon-a-very-important-foreign-visit-bjp-justifies-pms-5-nation-tour-amid-save-fuel-appeal-after-oppositions-wheres-modi-question%2Farticleshow%2F131174252.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A