ul%3E%3Cli%3EMarc%20Benioff%20said%20Slack's%20AI%20agent%20can%20identify%20what%20employees%20are%20upset%20about.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Salesforce%20CEO%20said%20the%20AI%20scans%20Slack%20chats%20to%20surface%20company%20concerns%20and%20key%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnything%20written%20on%20workplace%20Slack%20channels%20could%20be%20reviewed%20by%20employers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20Salesforce%20employee%20venting%20about%20work%20on%20Slack%2C%20CEO%20Marc%20Benioff%20may%20already%20know%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20Benioff%20touted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-salesforce-anthropic-spend-tokens-slack-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESlack's%20AI%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20way%20to%20analyze%20employees'%20conversations%2C%20surface%20frustrations%2C%20company%20concerns%2C%20and%20operational%20blind%20spots%20in%20real%20time.%20Salesforce%20acquired%20Slack%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20run%20your%20company%20on%20Slack%2C%20all%20your%20DMs%2C%20all%20your%20channels%2C%20we're%20reading%20that%20now%20through%20the%20AI%20and%20we%20can%20tell%20you%20more%20about%20your%20business%20than%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20told%20the%20interviewer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-marc-benioff-says-he-might-rename-company-agentforce-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebillionaire%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20personally%20uses%20Slackbot%20to%20query%20information%20about%20Salesforce%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20when%20I'm%20on%20Slackbot%2C%20I%20can%20ask%20it%20any%20question%20about%20my%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20my%20top%20five%20deals%3F%20What%20are%20my%20employees%20upset%20about%3F%20What%20are%20the%20top%20three%20things%20I%20need%20to%20focus%20on%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20boom%2C%20I%20get%20the%20information%20because%20it%20has%20the%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20leveraging%20AI%20to%20gather%20company%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-copilot-entertainment-purposes-terms-of-service-agreement-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintegrated%20Copilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20Teams%2C%20Outlook%2C%20Word%2C%20and%20Excel%2C%20allowing%20its%20AI%20assistant%20to%20summarize%20meetings%2C%20scan%20messages%2C%20identify%20action%20items%2C%20and%20answer%20questions%20using%20companywide%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20pursuing%20a%20similar%20strategy%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-stock-market-ai-trade-threaten-openai-nvidia-tsmc-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%20inside%20Workspace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20AI%20can%20analyze%20emails%2C%20documents%2C%20calendars%2C%20and%20chats%20to%20generate%20insights%20and%20automate%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20are%20also%20racing%20into%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlean%2C%20one%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20hottest%20enterprise%20AI%20startups%2C%20positions%20itself%20as%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglean-ai-startup-annual-recurring-revenue-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkplace%20search%20engine%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20pulls%20answers%20and%20insights%20from%20Slack%2C%20Google%20Drive%2C%20Jira%2C%20Confluence%2C%20and%20other%20internal%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenioff's%20comments%20also%20serve%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20workers%20should%20be%20cautious%20about%20what%20they%20say%20on%20workplace%20messaging%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegally%20and%20technically%2C%20employers%20generally%20own%20the%20data%20generated%20inside%20company%20Slack%20workspaces%20and%20can%20retain%2C%20export%2C%20and%20analyze%20messages%20depending%20on%20their%20subscription%20level%20and%20internal%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlack%20itself%20states%20in%20its%20privacy%20FAQs%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20Customer%20owns%20and%20controls%20all%20content%20submitted%20to%20their%20workspace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20employees%20should%20assume%20that%20anything%20written%20on%20work-provided%20communication%20platforms%2C%20including%20direct%20messages%2C%20could%20be%20accessed%2C%20retained%2C%20or%20reviewed%20by%20their%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20are%20increasingly%20using%20technology%20to%20monitor%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20Meta%20recently%20deployed%20internal%20tools%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-that-monitor-workers-can-use-data-train-ai-agents-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrack%20certain%20employee%20actions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20keystrokes%20and%20mouse%20movements%20%E2%80%94%20to%20help%20train%20AI%20agents%2C%20while%20Microsoft%20has%20added%20workplace%20tracking%20features%20to%20Teams%20that%20can%20automatically%20update%20employees'%20office%20locations%20based%20on%20company%20WiFi%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20has%20also%20used%20technology%20to%20track%20in-office%20attendance%2C%20while%20JPMorgan%20tracks%20software%20engineers'%20AI%20use%20via%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-ai-can-identify-upset-employees-from-slack-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779102271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0adbc5ecd7cc1332bb09b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-ai-can-identify-upset-emp