n%2C%20will%20be%20a%20proxy%20engagement%20involving%20Chinese%20military%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhangor-inside-the-5-billion-submarine-set-china-is-making-for-pakistan-11511860%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20tech%20exec%20sued%20Tesla%20over%20its%20Full%20Self-Driving%20promises%20%E2%80%94%20and%20won%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ben%20Gawiser%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07039294eb4c909fb2ccd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOracle%20exec%20Ben%20Gawiser%20behind%20the%20wheel%20of%20his%20Tesla%20Model%203.%3Cp%3EBen%20Gawiser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBen%20Gawiser%2C%20an%20Oracle%20executive%2C%20sued%20Tesla%20after%20waiting%20years%20for%20fully%20autonomous%20driving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGawiser%20is%20one%20of%20many%20Tesla%20owners%20whose%20vehicles%20are%20too%20old%20to%20support%20unsupervised%20full%20self-driving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20won%20over%20%2410%2C000%20in%20a%20default%20judgment%20after%20arguing%20that%20Tesla%20had%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20deliver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20came%20the%20self-driving%20dream.%20Then%20came%20the%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20EV%20maker%20has%20sold%20its%20cars%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20they%20would%20one%20day%20drive%20themselves.%20Last%20month%2C%20however%2C%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-tesla-hardware3-fully-autonomous-self-driving-trade-in-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20dropped%20a%20bombshell%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20told%20investors%20that%20some%20older%20Tesla%20vehicles%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20unsupervised%20Full%20Self-Driving%20(FSD)%20without%20a%20major%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20sparked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-tesla-owners-react-to-their-fsd-dreams-getting-crushed-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrustration%20and%20dismay%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20many%20longtime%20owners%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20paid%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20and%20waited%20years%20for%20fully%20autonomous%20FSD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Gawiser%2C%20a%20director%20of%20software%20engineering%20at%20Oracle%2C%20took%20matters%20into%20his%20own%20hands.%20The%20tech%20executive%20sued%20Tesla%20in%20a%20Texas%20small%20claims%20court%20earlier%20this%20year%20over%20its%20failure%20to%20deliver%20unsupervised%20Full%20Self-Driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20hearing%20on%20April%201%2C%20Gawiser%20was%20awarded%20%2410%2C600%20in%20a%20default%20judgment%20and%20%2472.88%20in%20court%20costs%20after%20Tesla%20failed%20to%20appear%20despite%20being%20notified%2C%20according%20to%20court%20records%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20month%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Tesla%20filed%20a%20motion%20asking%20the%20court%20to%20extend%20the%20appeal%20deadline%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20hearing%20or%20the%20default%20judgment.%20The%20judge%20denied%20Tesla's%20motion%2C%20according%20to%20court%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGawiser%2C%20who%20bought%20his%20Tesla%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-3-long-range-premium-review-pictures-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModel%203%20Long%20Range%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%202021%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20took%20legal%20action%20after%20becoming%20frustrated%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20communication%20from%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20literally%20had%20zero%20communication%20from%20them%2C%20pretty%20much%20since%20I%20bought%20the%20car.%20It%20has%20been%20complete%20radio%20silence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gawiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ben%20Gawiser%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0703cc94eb4c909fb2ccd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGawiser%20spent%20%2410%2C000%20on%20FSD%20when%20he%20bought%20his%20Tesla%20in%202021.%3Cp%3EBen%20Gawiser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Tesla%20%26quot%3Bfailed%26quot%3B%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20FSD%20promises.%26quot%3BI%20should%20get%20my%20money%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGawiser%20paid%20an%20extra%20%2410%2C000%20for%20FSD%20when%20he%20bought%20his%20car%20five%20years%20ago.%20The%20Austin%20resident%20shopped%20around%2C%20test-driving%20other%20EVs%20like%20Ford's%20Mustang%20Mach-E%2C%20but%20he%20said%20the%20promise%20of%20Tesla's%20advanced%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20including%20FSD%20%E2%80%94%20swayed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20wanted%20the%20Tesla%20because%20I%20wanted%20the%20tech%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gawiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20to%20think%20about%20taking%20action%20in%20January%202025%2C%20after%20Musk%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-earnings-call-report-tsla-stock-live-updates-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Tesla%20would%20likely%20have%20to%20upgrade%20older%20vehicles%20equipped%20with%20FSD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20attempts%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20company%20went%20nowhere%2C%20Gawiser%20filed%20a%20suit%20against%20Tesla%20in%20the%20small%20claims%20court%20in%20Travis%20County%2C%20Texas%2C%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20winning%20via%20a%20default%20judgment%2C%20Gawiser%20said%20he%20has%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20lawyers%20representing%20Tesla%2C%20asking%20how%20the%20company%20intends%20to%20pay%20the%20judgment.%20He%20added%20that%20if%20the%20company%20refuses%20to%20pay%2C%20he%20intends%20to%20ask%20the%20court%20for%20a%20writ%20of%20execution%2C%20which%2C%20if%20granted%2C%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20seize%20assets%20from%20one%20of%20Tesla's%20showrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a7e5fec-0f32-40ab-9ac6-34c44ca854f8%5C%22%3EFSD%20promises%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20back%20as%202016%2C%20Tesla%20has%20been%20selling%20its%20cars%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20they%20have%20the%20necessary%20hardware%20to%20eventually%20drive%20themselves%20at%20a%20safety%20level%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20greater%26quot%3B%20than%20a%20human%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Musk's%20self-driving%20ambitions%20have%20taken%20longer%20than%20expected%20to%20come%20to%20fruition%2C%20and%20the%20hardware%20in%20older%20models%20hasn't%20kept%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Tesla%20owners%20who%20bought%20their%20cars%20before%202023%20have%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20more%20limited%20version%20of%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-full-self-driving-review-limitations-fully-autonomous-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFull%20Self-Driving%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology%2C%20which%20Tesla%20says%20allows%20its%20cars%20to%20drive%20themselves%20almost%20anywhere%20but%20requires%20human%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Musk%20confirmed%20that%20Tesla%20vehicles%20with%20pre-2023%20hardware%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20unsupervised%20version%20of%20FSD%2C%20which%20Tesla%20has%20deployed%20in%20its%20robotaxi%20service%20in%20Texas%20but%20has%20not%20yet%20made%20available%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20CEO%20said%20customers%20would%20be%20offered%20a%20discounted%20trade-in%20or%20a%20full%20overhaul%20of%20their%20car's%20AI%20computer%20and%20cameras%2C%20which%20would%20require%20the%20company%20to%20set%20up%20%26quot%3Bmicro-factories%26quot%3B%20outside%20major%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20already%20been%20hit%20with%20several%20lawsuits%20in%20the%20US%20over%20what%20owners%20have%20described%20as%20misleading%20FSD%20advertising%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20also%20facing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-tesla-owners-react-to-their-fsd-dreams-getting-crushed-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20legal%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20European%20customers%20after%20the%20supervised%20version%20of%20the%20software%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-owners-fsd-europe-full-self-driving-netherlands-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%20in%20the%20Netherlands%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20executives%20have%20said%20they%20plan%20to%20release%20a%20%26quot%3Blite%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20FSD%20software%20update%20for%20older%20vehicle%20owners%2C%20expected%20in%20June%2C%20which%20will%20also%20be%20available%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20now%2C%20pre-2023%20Tesla%20owners%20are%20stuck%20with%20a%20limited%20version%20of%20the%20company's%20flagship%20software%2C%20with%20fully%20autonomous%20driving%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGawiser%20said%20that%20he%20has%20largely%20stopped%20using%20FSD%20after%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%20involving%20the%20tech%2C%20including%20his%20Tesla%20failing%20to%20slow%20down%20in%20school%20zones%20and%20coming%20to%20a%20halt%20for%20no%20apparent%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ben%20Gawiser%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a070472ecd7cc1332bb000f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGawiser%20said%20despite%20his%20dispute%20with%20Tesla%2C%20he's%20still%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20his%20Model%203.%3Cp%3EBen%20Gawiser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oracle%20executive%20said%20that%2C%20having%20worked%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20for%20years%2C%20he%20bought%20his%20Tesla%20with%20the%20knowledge%20that%20new%20technology%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20come%20to%20fruition%20%E2%80%94%20but%20said%20that%20didn't%20excuse%20what%20he%20sees%20as%20Tesla's%20and%20Musk's%20failure%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20CEO%20should%20set%20a%20visionary%20goal%20for%20the%20company.%20But%20don't%20put%20it%20in%20the%20contract%20with%20your%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Gawiser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20people%20who%20bought%20around%20the%20time%20that%20I%20bought%20and%20paid%20for%20full%20self-driving%2C%20I%20think%20they%20have%20no%20trust%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20dispute%20with%20the%20company%2C%20Gawiser%20said%20he%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20giving%20up%20his%20Model%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20car.%20It's%20a%20great%20car.%20It's%20the%20best%20car%20that%20I've%20ever%20owned.%20And%20if%20it%20wasn't%20made%20by%20Tesla%2C%20I%20would%20totally%20buy%20another%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-exec-sued-tesla-full-self-driving-promises-model-3-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779101154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07039294eb4c909fb2ccd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-exec-sued-tesla-full-self-driving-promises-model-3-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla's%20FSD%20rollbacks%20have%20sparked%20frustration%20among%20many%20long-time%20owners%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20paid%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20for%20fully%20autonomous%20driving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22c