s%20testing%20a%20new%20simulation%20software%20to%20train%20its%20tax%20staffers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tool%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20workers%20build%20the%20judgment%20that%20once%20came%20from%20years%20of%20grunt%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHigh-volume%2C%20high-speed%20simulations%20can%20help%20workers%20build%20skills%20faster%2C%20an%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20KPMG%20US%2C%20workers%20might%20no%20longer%20need%20years%20of%20hands-on%2C%20repetitive%20work%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-pilot-tax-pros-vibe-code-software-tools-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20good%20at%20tax%20prep%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20testing%20an%20AI-powered%20simulation%20tool%20designed%20to%20help%20employees%20build%20the%20skills%20they%20once%20gained%20through%20years%20of%20pencil%20pushing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20allow%20junior%20staffers%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20tax%20prep%20as%20AI%20begins%20to%20take%20over%20tasks%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20Brad%20Brown%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20digital%20officer%20for%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20as%20many%20repetitions%20of%20doing%20that%20task%20as%20you%20would%20have%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20needed%20something%20to%20fill%20that%20void.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-dashboard-consultants-ai-adoption-use-tracker-employees-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Brown%20said%2C%20an%20early-career%20tax%20professional%20at%20the%20company%20typically%20spent%20about%20four%20years%20preparing%20returns%20for%20clients%2C%20one%20after%20another.%20The%20repetition%20built%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20staffers%20gained%20experience%2C%20they%20could%20become%20more%20like%20advisors%2C%20offering%20guidance%20on%20the%20interplay%20between%20business%20decisions%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20tax%20consequences%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20tool%2C%20called%20TaxSIM%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-revamping-audit-internship-emphasize-judgment-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehelp%20workers%20develop%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20rapidly%26quot%3B%20through%20high-volume%2C%20high-speed%20simulation%2C%20without%20having%20to%20prepare%20as%20many%20returns%20from%20scratch%2C%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20will%20be%20available%20to%20the%20company's%2010%2C000%20tax%20staffers%20later%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG's%20approach%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%20that's%20hanging%20over%20large%20swaths%20of%20white-collar%20work%3A%20What%20happens%20when%20AI%20takes%20over%20the%20rote%20tasks%20that%20help%20people%20develop%20their%20skills%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20behind%20the%20AI%20training%20is%20similar%20to%20how%20the%20game%20%26quot%3BGran%20Turismo%26quot%3B%20simulates%20zipping%20around%20a%20Formula%201%20course%2C%20said%20Kes%20Sampanthar%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Centaurian%20AI%2C%20which%20developed%20the%20tool%20with%20KPMG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20the%20top%20athlete%20who%20gets%20better%20and%20better%20if%20they%20can%20get%20the%20right%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdf6d791-378b-4740-bb48-5c946cc6dd31%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Incredible%20acceleration'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20waiting%20perhaps%20years%20to%20encounter%20different%20client%20situations%2C%20tax%20workers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-survey-ceos-ai-spending-hiring-plans-cybersecurity-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Big%20Four%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20able%20to%20cycle%20through%20simulated%20scenarios.%20The%20tool%20presents%20different%20results%20based%20on%20users'%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20just%20gives%20us%20incredible%20acceleration%20to%20create%20those%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20some%20early-career%20workers%20are%20expressing%20concern%20about%20how%20they'll%20build%20their%20skills%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-canva-meta-tell-some-job-candidates-ok-use-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20takes%20on%20more%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20need%20to%20continually%20learn%20%26quot%3Bcuts%20across%20every%20rung%20of%20the%20ladder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20experienced%20workers%20who%20use%20the%20tool%20can%20dig%20into%20broad%20concepts%2C%20including%20changing%20economic%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20how%20tariffs%20ripple%20through%20organizations%20and%20countries%2C%20said%20Sampanthar%2C%20who's%20also%20a%20KPMG%20alum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20things%20you%20normally%20don't%20get%20feedback%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESampanthar%20said%20that%2C%20for%20any%20user%2C%20the%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20prompt%20them%20to%20work%20through%20their%20own%20reasoning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-analyst-quit-job-over-concerns-ai-would-replace-them-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebefore%20turning%20to%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20help.%20Some%20simulations%20can't%20be%20done%20with%20AI%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLearning%20happens%20when%20things%20are%20hard%2C%20not%20when%20things%20are%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277de9857-cb63-444a-be95-04fffb009a93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelping%20junior%20workers%20move%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20tool%20to%20accelerate%20the%20development%20of%20workers'%20analytical%20skills%2C%20helping%20some%20employees%20move%20up%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20that%20might%20entail%20managing%20a%20team%20of%20AI%20agents%20and%20less%20time%20spent%20%26quot%3Bworking%20these%20tasks%20yourself%20through%20the%20midnight%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it's%20a%20reminder%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-job-build-ai-skills-help-change-roles-employers-hiring-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkers%20who%20can%20use%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20alongside%20their%20judgment%20and%20analytic%20skills%20will%20be%20most%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20AI%20simulations%20will%20replace%20every%20task%2C%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20first-year%20tax%20analyst%20recently%20told%20him%20about%20wanting%20to%20build%20their%20first%20valuation%20model%20by%20hand%20before%20learning%20through%20simulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20person's%20thinking%2C%20Brown%20said%2C%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20OK%20to%20do%20one%20or%20two%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20four%20years%20of%20these%20to%20get%20to%20that%20level%20of%20skill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-training-tax-workers-through-simulation-tool-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779097501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a066bc494eb4c909fb2cb6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-training-tax-workers-through-simula