era-woman-saves-3-children-from-burning-building-she-doesnt-make-it-11511449%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-prayagraj-fire-on-camera-woman-saves-3-children-from-burning-building-she-doesnt-make-it-11511449%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-prayagraj-fire-on-camera-woman-saves-3-children-from-burning-building-she-doesnt-make-it-11511449%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20is%20hiring%20workers%20to%20reduce%20'friction'%20in%20communities%20where%20it's%20building%20data%20centers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20in%20St.%20Paul%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20attend%20data%20center%20moratorium%20now%20rally.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a368a94eb4c909fb2d569%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECommunities%20across%20America%20are%20pushing%20back%20against%20data%20center%20development.%3Cp%3EUCG%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20is%20hiring%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommunity%20engagement%20lead%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20Stargate%20team.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20role%20will%20act%20as%20a%20liaison%20between%20OpenAI%20and%20the%20communities%20where%20it's%20building%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmericans%20are%20clashing%20with%20local%20governments%20and%20tech%20companies%20over%20data%20center%20developments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20needs%20help%20reversing%20the%20American%20public's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgallup-opposition-data-centers-nuclear-reactors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esouring%20view%20of%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leading%20AI%20company%20shared%20a%20new%20job%20opening%20over%20the%20weekend%20for%20a%20position%20it%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommunity%20engagement%20lead.%26quot%3B%20These%20new%20employees%20would%20be%20tasked%20with%20talking%20to%20local%20communities%20in%20places%20where%20it%20plans%20to%20build%20its%20Stargate%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20measure%20of%20success%2C%20it%20said%2C%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Breduced%20friction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20are%20investing%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20building%20data%20centers%20to%20power%20their%20products.%20Local%20communities%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20always%20so%20welcoming.%20Many%20residents%20worry%20that%20the%20data%20centers%20will%20drain%20water%20supplies%2C%20raise%20electric%20bills%2C%20cause%20noise%2C%20and%20just%C2%A0generally%20reduce%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20companies%20argue%20that%20they%20can%20mitigate%20some%20of%20these%20problems%20by%20adopting%20new%20cooling%20techniques%20and%20paying%20for%20their%20own%20electricity%20costs.%20They%20also%20say%20these%20projects%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-utah-data-center-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreate%20thousands%20of%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20local%20communities%2C%20though%20many%20of%20those%20jobs%20are%20in%20the%20construction%20phase%2C%20which%20means%20they%20are%20temporary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProtests%20have%20arisen%20across%20the%20country%20as%20communities%20push%20back.%20Prominent%20businessmen%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20investor%20Kevin%20O'Leary%2C%20who%20is%20backing%20a%20data%20center%20development%20in%20Utah%2C%20have%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-blames-paid-activists-for-utah-data-center-protests-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintense%20opposition%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20data%20centers%20is%20a%20near%20existential%20requirement%20for%20AI%20companies%2C%20whose%20ever-advancing%20chatbots%20and%20agents%20require%20ever-growing%20amounts%20of%20data%20to%20work%20effectively.%20Some%20companies%2C%20like%20Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%2C%20are%20exploring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-hiring-elon-musk-data-centers-in-space-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20them%20in%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Stargate%20project%20%E2%80%94%20a%20partnership%20between%20OpenAI%2C%20Oracle%2C%20SoftBank%2C%20and%20MGX%20%E2%80%94%20was%20announced%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20the%20day%20after%20he%20began%20his%20second%20term.%20The%20group%20plans%20to%20invest%20%24500%20billion%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStargate%20data%20centers%20are%20now%20planned%20in%20Texas%2C%20Michigan%2C%20New%20Mexico%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20job%20posting%20for%20the%20community%20engagement%20lead%2C%20OpenAI%20says%20that%20getting%20communities%20on%20board%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-saline-michigan-funding-openai-stargate-blackstone-pimco-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethese%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20%26quot%3Bmission-critical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20role%20ensures%20that%20communities%20understand%20what%20we%20are%20building%2C%20why%20it%20matters%2C%20and%20how%20they%20can%20meaningfully%20benefit%20from%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20potential%20candidates%20will%20be%20required%20to%20be%20based%20in%2C%20or%20willing%20to%20relocate%20to%2C%20communities%20where%20OpenAI%20is%20building%20data%20center%20sites.%20The%20job%20pays%20between%20%24129%2C600%20and%20%24236%2C000%2C%20plus%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Community%20Engagement%20Lead%20will%20proactively%20shape%20dialogue%2C%20surface%20concerns%20before%20they%20escalate%2C%20and%20embed%20community%20priorities%20into%20how%20projects%20are%20planned%2C%20communicated%2C%20and%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-jobs-ai-data-center-opposition-community-engagement2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779096661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a369babc4e9d88574ae11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-jobs-ai-data-center-opposition-community-engagement2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20says%20it%20will%20pay%20someone%20up%20to%20%24236%2C000%20plus%20equity%20to%20help%20reduce%20tensions%20in%20communities%20where%20they%20are%20developing%20Stargate%20data%20centers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20BBC%20Boss%20Matt%20Brittin%20Warns%20Staff%20%E2%80%98Tough%20Choices%20Are%20Unavoidable%20as%20We%20Make%20Savings%E2%80%99%20on%20First%20Day%20in%20the%20Job%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779096643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236752178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20new%20director%20general%20Matt%20Brittin%20has%20warned%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctough%20choices%20are%20unavoidable%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20first%20memo%20to%20staff.%20Describing%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Clifelong%20fan%20of%20the%20BBC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20Google%20executive%20opened%20the%20missive%20by%20saying%20that%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20he%20has%20been%20meeting%20teams%20in%20England%2C%20Wales%2C%20Scotland%2C%20Northern%20Ireland%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22K.J.%20Yossman%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnA