a%20Bozieva%20created%20a%2027%20AI%20agent%20workflow%20to%20run%20her%20company.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Linara%20Bozieva%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELinara%20Bozieva%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20eBay%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20founded%20a%20growth%20marketing%20agency%20and%20built%20a%20three-layer%20AI%20workflow%20with%2027%20custom%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20her%20AI%20subscriptions%20cost%20under%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Linara%20Bozieva%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20founder%20of%20Ravenopous%2C%20based%20in%20San%20Jose.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20over%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-layoffs-impact-1000-workers-ceo-memo-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20from%20eBay%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20spending%2011%20years%20with%20the%20company.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20had%20recently%20moved%20from%20Switzerland%20to%20the%20US%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20hard%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20the%20job%20market%20and%20saw%20that%20many%20companies%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-us-these-are-companies-making-cuts-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaying%20off%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20more%20candidates%20than%20openings.%20It%20felt%20worth%20it%20to%20start%20building%20something%20small%2C%20at%20least%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20to%20support%20my%20family%20and%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20my%20layoff%20in%202024%2C%20I%20launched%20a%20traditional%20marketing%20agency.%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20marketing%20background%2C%20but%20I%20built%20a%20three-layer%20AI%20workflow%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-steve-jobs-custom-gpt-to-make-my-business-decisions-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E27%20custom%20AI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20run%20an%20entire%20marketing%20strategy%20under%20my%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20talk%20to%20founders%20of%20AI-powered%20companies%20with%20fewer%20than%2010%20workers%2C%20and%20to%20employees%20working%20alongside%20AI%20agents%2C%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20%26quot%3BTiny%20Teams%26quot%3B%20era%20really%20feels%20like%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wins%2C%20the%20fears%2C%20and%20the%20human%20skills%20that%20stand%20out.%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20filling%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScO-Lptuw9eirYFmkAfOKc1aOvrFIW1jT2FzxuLJSexsTLExg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1ab6132-5a11-4d77-a68e-72355143e53f%5C%22%3EMy%20professional%20background%20helped%20me%20automate%20my%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20AI%20became%20mainstream%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-startup-founder-switched-chatgpt-to-claude-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20used%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20my%20browser%3Cstrong%3E%3Cs%3E%20%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20tools%20like%20Midjourney%20for%20video%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20started%20seeing%20how%20people%20were%20using%20AI%20in%20these%20closed-loop%20systems%2C%20where%20agents%20acted%20autonomously%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20originally%20built%20my%20system%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-agent-smith-employees-ai-driven-coding-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Antigravity%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20was%20very%20user-friendly%2C%20but%20I%20eventually%20switched%20to%20Claude%20Code%20after%20running%20into%20token%20limits%20with%20Gemini%20Pro.%20I%20love%20Claude%2C%20but%20I%20have%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-usage-caps-changes-popularity-anthropic-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehitting%20token%20limits%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20in%20analytics%20at%20eBay%2C%20and%20that%20background%20helped%20when%20I%20was%20building%20the%20architecture%20and%20creating%20guidelines.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20AI%20wrote%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20system%20itself.%20With%20all%20the%20markdown%20files%2C%20skills%2C%20agent%20files%2C%20and%20scripts%2C%20I%20told%20the%20model%20what%20I%20wanted%20it%20to%20do%20in%20plain%20language%2C%20the%20AI%20produced%20it%2C%20and%20then%20I%20tweaked%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4caaebe-329c-46e8-9609-86938d5a6769%5C%22%3EHere's%20how%20my%2027%20AI%20agents%20function%20on%20my%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20automated%20system%20has%20three%20layers%3A%20directives%2C%20orchestration%2C%20and%20execution.%20The%20directives%20layer%20defines%20who%20the%20agents%20are%2C%20what%20they%20know%2C%20and%20how%20they%20operate.%20The%20orchestration%20layer%20decides%20which%20agents%20should%20do%20what%20and%20when.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20six%20agents%20in%20the%20orchestration%20layer%20that%20act%20as%20the%20brain%20and%20think%20before%20any%20other%20agents%20act.%20Those%20agents%20are%20a%20market%20researcher%20agent%2C%20a%20data%20analyst%20agent%2C%20a%20creative%20director%20agent%2C%20a%20finance%20agent%2C%20a%20legal%20agent%2C%20and%20an%20orchestrator%20agent%20that%20routes%20tasks%20to%20the%20execution%20layer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20tasks%20are%20routed%2C%20three%20agents%20build%20the%20technical%20groundwork%2C%2010%20work%20on%20driving%20traffic%20and%20awareness%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-management-structure-org-chart-consulting-firms-mckinsey-ibm-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20last%20five%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20responsible%20for%20converting%20traffic%20into%20revenue.%20The%20execution%20layer%20includes%20scripts%20that%20help%20guide%20repeatable%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20setup%20costs%20me%20under%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%20I'm%20paying%20for%20Claude%20Code%2C%20Codex%2C%20and%20ChatGPT.%20Then%20I%20have%20a%20few%20specialized%20tools%20like%20HeyGen%20and%20ElevenLabs%2C%20and%20I'm%20paying%20for%20APIs%20because%20I'm%20also%20giving%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswitched-from-chatgpt-to-claude-how-ceo-uses-both-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20access%20to%20other%20models%20and%20tools%20through%20APIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230ac4772-f153-4076-a0f3-965c62259e3c%5C%22%3EThe%20hardest%20part%20was%20knowing%20when%20the%20system%20actually%20worked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20has%20now%20been%20trained%20on%2014%20clients%20in%20total.%20I%20currently%20have%20five%20clients%2C%20but%20I%20also%20tested%20the%20workflow%20on%20my%20own%20projects%20and%20did%20free%20work%20for%20friends%20to%20improve%20the%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20challenging%20thing%20was%20knowing%20when%20the%20system%20was%20operational.%20Which%20is%20why%20I%20tested%20it%20on%2014%20client%20profiles.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20system%20fully%20understood%20my%20approach%20and%20frameworks%20and%20delivered%20high-quality%20results%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20I%20now%20have%20Gemini%20and%20Claude%20generate%20my%20ad%20copy%20separately%2C%20then%20compare%20and%20combine%20the%20results%20to%20get%20something%20that%20feels%20more%20human.%20The%20final%20best%20copy%20is%20produced%20from%20their%20combined%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20added%20scripts%20in%20the%20execution%20layer%20that%20pull%20customer%20pain%20points%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-ceo-platform-most-human-place-on-internet-ai-slop-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReddit%20discussions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sharpen%20the%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288154787-c1c7-4ea8-a02f-c1327bee6779%5C%22%3ESocial%20skills%20are%20what%20I've%20realized%20to%20be%20very%20valuable%20in%20the%20AI%20era%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-founder-runs-company-with-15-ai-agents-heres-how-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20run%20ads%2C%20analyze%20performance%2C%20improve%20creatives%2C%20and%20then%20give%20me%20daily%20reports.%20The%20client%20gets%20weekly%20reports%2C%20and%20we%20do%20broader%20monthly%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20can%20process%20a%20transcript%20of%20a%20client%20call%2C%20but%20it%20cannot%20fully%20read%20the%20room%20or%20identify%20where%20the%20client%20seems%20most%20nervous.%20That%20judgment%20and%20client%20management%20still%20have%20to%20come%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20heavily%20involved%20in%20the%20strategy%20when%20there%20isn't%20enough%20incoming%20data%2C%20and%20my%20agent%20and%20I%20are%20at%20a%20crossroads%20about%20which%20path%20to%20choose.%20I%20continually%20check%20if%20what%20the%20agents%20propose%20really%20makes%20sense%20and%20is%20realistically%20doable%20as%20a%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20AI%20can%20build%20you%20a%20system%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20domain.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20build%20a%20healthcare%20agent%20that%20treats%20colds%20and%20flu%20in%20children%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20that%20knowledge%20and%20wouldn't%20know%20which%20guidelines%20to%20include%20and%20which%20agents%20I%20would%20need%2C%20or%20how%20to%20better%20update%20the%20system%20as%20I%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20all%20repetitive%20tasks%20can%20and%20will%20be%20done%20by%20AI%20in%20the%20future.%20However%2C%20the%20expertise%20needed%20for%20specific%20departments%20or%20domains%20will%20still%20be%20with%20humans%20acting%20as%20VPs%20over%20AI%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232cf291e-34d7-4e19-9662-8d4a03196703%5C%22%3EAI%20changed%20what%20I%20believe%20is%20possible%20for%20one%20person%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20have%20a%20few%20traditional%20marketing%20clients%20that%20I%20serve%20with%20my%20freelancers.%20Since%20we've%20been%20serving%20them%20before%2C%20we%20can't%20say%20we%20aren't%20doing%20that%20anymore.%20It's%20a%20smaller%2C%20separate%20branch%20of%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20new%20clients%20I%20take%20on%2C%20I%20now%20provide%20only%20full-cycle%20marketing%20through%20the%20AI%20system.%20Once%20a%20client%20is%20fully%20onboarded%2C%20I%20spend%20about%20two%20hours%20a%20week%20overseeing%20their%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20focused%20only%20on%20client%20oversight%2C%20I%20think%20I%20could%20comfortably%20manage%2020%20to%2025%20clients%20on%20my%20own.%20Once%20I%20reach%20that%20number%2C%20I'll%20only%20hire%20people%20like%20me%2C%20operators%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanager-oversees-ai-agents-that-help-do-work-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoversee%20the%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20guide%20the%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20something%20on%20my%20own%20has%20been%20incredibly%20fulfilling%20and%20promising.%20It%20changed%20not%20just%20how%20I%20work%2C%20but%20what%20I%20believe%20one%20person%20can%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20working%20with%20mostly%20AI%20agents%3F%20If%20so%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20at%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-founded-a-business-with-27-ai-agent-employees-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779095461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05f3e894eb4c909fb2c868%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-founded-a-business-with-27-ai-agent-employees-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20being%20laid%20off%20from%20eBay%2C%20Linara%20Bozieva%20launched%20an%20AI-powered%20marketing%20agency%20which%20she%20runs%20with%2027%20custom%20AI%20agents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aapplegate%40insider.com%20(Agnes%20Applegate)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meghan%20Markle%E2%80%99s%20all-black%20fit%20for%20Geneva%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779095169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131171722%2Cimgsize-99136.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fmeghan-markle-nails-power-dressing-in-sleek-all-black-suit-for-lost-screen-memorial-inauguration-in-geneva%2Farticleshow%2F131171722.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131171722.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20Geneva%2C%20Meghan%20Markle%20dazzled%20in%20an%20elegant%20all-black%20outfit%20during%20the%20inauguration%20of%20The%20Lost%20Screen%20Memorial.%20Her%20impactful%20speech%20at%20the%20World%20Health%20Assembly%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20children%20to%20online%20violence%2C%20calling%20on%20tech%20companies%20to%20take%20