gside%20Ankita%20Walawalkar%20and%20Prajakta%20Mali%2C%20proudly%20showcased%20Maharashtrian%20culture%2C%20particularly%20with%20their%20traditional%20'Nath'%20adornments.%20Actor%20Pushkar%20Jog%20also%20graced%20the%20event%2C%20celebrating%20the%20global%20launch%20of%20OTT%20platform%20Abhijat%20Marathi%20and%20adding%20a%20distinct%20cultural%20flavor%20to%20the%20international%20festival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20are%20kicking%20off%20a%20mad%20cybersecurity%20dash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20and%20Dario%20Amodei%20in%20a%20split-frame.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a079f3a94eb4c909fb2d24f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Bloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic's%20Mythos%20and%20OpenAI's%20GPT-5.5%20sparked%20major%20cybersecurity%20concerns%20worldwide.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20rise%20in%20AI%20coding%20heightens%20vulnerability%20to%20cyber%20attacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESecurity%20professionals%20are%20working%20overtime%20to%20address%20the%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CISO%2C%20or%20chief%20information%20security%20officer%2C%20has%20suddenly%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20high-pressure%20roles%20in%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20spring%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-mythos-cybersecurity-concerns-what-smart-people-are-saying-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Mythos%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-openai-exclusive-launch-party-chatgpt-planned-itself-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20GPT%E2%80%915.5%20%3C%2Fa%3Emodels%20sparked%20a%20wave%20of%20fear%20that%20attackers%20armed%20with%20advanced%20AI%20models%20could%20soon%20crack%20systems%20worldwide.%20And%20the%20unease%20adds%20to%20the%20issues%20that%20cybersecurity%20already%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20companies%20use%20outside%20code%20libraries%20than%20in%20eras%20prior%2C%20which%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20hacks%20to%20spread%20if%20there%20are%20vulnerabilities%20in%20those%20packages%20of%20code.%20And%20last%20year%2C%20coding%20tools%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-unlikely-crowd-retirees-children-teens-non-technical-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20off%2C%20helping%20developers%20churn%20out%20millions%20of%20lines%20of%20new%20code.%20Those%20tools%20are%20prone%20to%20creating%20errors%20and%20vulnerabilities%20that%20developers%20miss%20%E2%80%94%20putting%20researchers%2C%20companies%2C%20and%20governments%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone's%20predicting%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20hacking%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Isaac%20Evans%2C%20CEO%20of%20cybersecurity%20startup%20Semgrep.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAn%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20pointed%20to%20a%20recent%20spree%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fcybersecurity-in-the-intelligence-age%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyber-focused%20announcements%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fcodex-security-now-in-research-preview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleases%20that%20aim%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20AI%20improvements%20help%20defenders%20work%20more%20quickly%20and%20effectively.%20The%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fdaybreak%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDaybreak%26quot%3B%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20lets%20developers%20request%20a%20security%20scan.%20Anthropic%2C%20which%20is%20also%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20cybersecurity%20push%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223335ae6e-c582-409a-b44a-6e17ef75cbb7%5C%22%3EBefore%20Anthropic%20announced%20Mythos%2C%20security%20pros%20were%20already%20overburdened%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvans'%20startup%20focuses%20on%20code%20security%20and%20operates%20a%20free%2C%20widely%20used%20code-scanning%20tool.%20He%20said%20that%20a%20recent%20threat%20prompted%20his%20company%20to%20scour%20its%20codebase%20for%20vulnerabilities%2C%20and%20the%20team%20found%20two%20%E2%80%94%20both%20contributed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-engineer-claude-boris-cherny-ai-agent-use-overnight-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20drawback%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-code-creator-boris-cherny-vibe-coding-anthropic-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-coding%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Evans%20said%20if%20a%20company%20generates%2010%20times%20the%20lines%20of%20code%2C%20it%20should%20expect%2010%20times%20the%20number%20of%20vulnerabilities%2C%20or%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeross%20Aboukhadijeh%2C%20CEO%20of%20cybersecurity%20startup%20Socket%2C%20reiterated%20Evans'%20worries%20about%20developers%20reviewing%20new%20code%20less%20carefully.%20That%2C%20plus%20using%20outside%20code%20libraries%20to%20complement%20a%20company's%20internal%20code%2C%20creates%20a%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20storm%26quot%3B%20of%20danger%2C%20Aboukhadijeh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpen-source%20code%20libraries%20are%20often%20well-maintained%2C%20following%20the%20principle%20that%20transparency%20helps%20remove%20bugs.%20Now%2C%20so%20many%20companies%20use%20code%20from%20these%20repositories%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-admits-claude-code-issues-user-complaints-denies-nerfing-degrading-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20pull%20from%20them%20%E2%80%94%20that%20a%20single%20security%20gap%20can%20imperil%20many%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vulnerability%20surface%20of%20all%20software%20is%20expanding%20really%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Aboukhadijeh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22310d5b75-b2f6-4b09-af74-b5b48d58b65f%5C%22%3EThe%20%26quot%3BMythos%20Moment%26quot%3B%20triggered%20a%20reckoning%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20for%20security%20teams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%20teams%20already%20use%20new%20AI%20models%20to%20search%20for%20vulnerabilities%20while%20also%20worrying%20about%20attackers%20gaining%20access%20to%20models%20of%20similar%20strength.%20Then%2C%20on%20April%207%2C%20came%20what's%20now%20being%20called%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-mythos-preview-anthropic-cybersecurity-reaction-glasswing-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMythos%20Moment%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20day%2C%20Anthropic%20announced%20that%20its%20new%20general-purpose%20AI%20model%2C%20dubbed%20Mythos%2C%20had%20found%20thousands%20of%20severe%20security%20vulnerabilities%2C%20some%20that%20humans%20had%20missed%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20While%20it%20identified%20vulnerabilities%2C%20it%20could%20also%20exploit%20%26quot%3Bevery%20major%20operating%20system%20and%20every%20major%20web%20browser%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20engineers%20at%20the%20lab%20had%20used%20the%20technology%20to%20find%20working%20hacks%20over%20a%20single%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20decided%20not%20to%20release%20the%20model%20beyond%20a%20group%20of%20trusted%20partners%2C%20giving%20defenders%20a%20head%20start.%20The%20Mythos%20announcement%20put%20it%20plainly%3A%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20it's%20about%20to%20become%20very%20difficult%20for%20the%20security%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20warning%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it'd%20made%20a%20model%20too%20dangerous%20to%20immediately%20release%20%E2%80%94%20reverberated%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-react-government-trump-vetting-ai-models-regulation-innovation-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20discussing%20a%20system%20to%20review%20new%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUK%20government%20officials%20also%20released%20an%20open%20letter%20about%20Mythos%2C%20warning%20businesses%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20your%20board%20has%20not%20recently%20discussed%20cyber%20risk%2C%20do%20so%20at%20your%20next%20meeting%20and%20then%20regularly.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20to%20delegate%20to%20your%20IT%20team%20and%20forget%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20corporate%20world's%20security%20community%20leaped%20into%20action%2C%20either%20hunting%20for%20Mythos%20access%20or%20racing%20to%20test%20it.%20Some%20early%20reviews%20affirmed%20Anthropic's%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20team%20at%20Mozilla%2C%20the%20organization%20behind%20Firefox%2C%20wrote%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmozilla-anthropic-mythos-hundreds-flaws-fuzzers-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMythos%20helped%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20find%20and%20fix%20more%20security%20bugs%20than%20they%20had%20in%20the%20previous%20year.%20Researchers%20with%20the%20security%20firm%20Calif%C2%A0say%C2%A0Mythos%20helped%20them%20identify%20bugs%20in%20MacOS%2C%20link%20them%20together%2C%20and%20ultimately%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20corrupt%20part%20of%20the%20famously%20secure%20technology.%20(Apple%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20though%20it%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20it%20is%20reviewing%20the%20findings.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECybersecurity%20giants%20like%20CrowdStrike%2C%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%2C%20and%20Fortinet%20have%20each%20posted%20recent%20announcements%20warning%20about%20the%20potential%20dangers%20of%20frontier%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManoj%20Nair%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20emerging%20technologies%20and%20solutions%20office%20at%20the%20security%20startup%20Snyk%2C%20said%20that%20with%20Mythos%20and%20OpenAI's%20GPT-5.5%20landing%20on%20top%20of%20other%20security%20issues%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20CISO%20today%2C%20you're%20living%20in%20what%20I%20call%20the%20'AI%20fog'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENair's%20company%2C%20like%20Socket%20and%20Semgrep%2C%20has%20signed%20onto%20a%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI%20to%20try%20to%20beat%20back%20the%20storm%20of%20worries.%20Anthropic%20is%20also%20hatching%20these%20partnerships%2C%20giving%20companies%20like%20Snyk%20a%20chance%20to%20try%20out%20the%20advanced%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELogan%20Graham%2C%20who%20heads%20Anthropic's%20frontier%20red%20team%2C%20recently%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20his%20cybersecurity%20team%20is%20bringing%20Mythos%20%26quot%3Bto%20defenders%20as%20fast%20as%20we%20responsibly%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecurity%20is%20always%20a%20team%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20Nair%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20model%20companies%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20is%20how%20security%20works.%20And%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ascouncil%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Escouncil%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20over%20text%2C%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20415-757-8198.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fs