-vc-investors-2026-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeed%2040%3C%2Fa%3E%20lists%20based%20on%20data%20analyzed%20by%20Termina.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETermina%20began%20with%20data%20on%201%2C974%20investors%20and%20analyzed%2025%20success%20attributes%2C%20including%20exits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20analysis%20identifies%20skilled%20investors%20with%20a%20high%20likelihood%20of%20continued%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeed%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-40-best-women-early-stage-vc-investors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeed%2040%3C%2Fa%3E%20lists%20have%20reached%20their%20sixth%20year%20in%20our%20partnership%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20objectively%20identifies%20and%20celebrates%20the%20success%20of%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20greatest%20seed%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20of%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeed%20100%20releases%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20AI%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20defining%20characteristic%20of%20seed-stage%20startups%20today%2C%20with%20results%20that%20will%20likely%20drive%20the%20rankings%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20produce%20the%202026%20lists%2C%20we%20statistically%20analyzed%20seed%20investor%20performance%20in%2025%20areas%20using%20Crunchbase%20and%20PitchBook%20data.%20We%20also%20accept%20direct%20track%20record%20submissions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.termina.ai%2Fseed-100%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20aim%20to%20analyze%20the%20potential%20success%20of%20investors%20rather%20than%20focus%20solely%20on%20past%20achievements%2C%20we%20consider%20only%20active%20investors%20with%20at%20least%20five%20investments%20between%202011%20and%202026.%20Our%20list%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-capitalists-startup-investors-shaking-up-venture-capital-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esolo%20venture%20capitalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-are-the-60-top-angel-investors-for-b2b-startups-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eangel%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20worldwide%2C%20assessed%20based%20on%20their%20investments%20in%20US%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investors%20that%20made%20the%20cut%20for%20the%202026%20Seed%20100%20were%20those%20with%20the%20strongest%20long-term%20indicators%3A%20exits%20(IPOs%20or%20acquisitions).%20Investors%20with%20a%20previous%20AI%20footprint%20have%20benefited%20significantly%20in%20their%20rankings%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20named%20to%20the%20list%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-investors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseed%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20must%20have%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvestments%20that%20led%20to%20successful%20exits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20including%20successful%20IPOs%20or%20acquisitions%20(exits%20that%20were%20meaningfully%20above%20%26quot%3Bliquidation%20preference%26quot%3B%20or%20demonstrated%20increased%20company%20value%20rather%20than%20simply%20raising%20capital).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntermediate%20signs%20of%20future%20success%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseed%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%20consistently%20receiving%20material%20sums%20of%20follow-on%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStill%20be%20in%20the%20game.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGreat%20investments%2010%20years%20ago%20will%20not%20carry%20an%20investor%20into%20the%20list%20if%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20active.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EExits%20(IPOs%20or%20acquisitions)%20statistically%20have%20the%20greatest%20influence%20on%20investor%20differentiation.%20We%20also%20updated%20our%20methodology%20this%20year%20to%20weigh%20more%20recent%20investments%20for%20the%20intermediate%20milestones%2C%20such%20as%20follow-on%20fundraising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20candidate%20pool%20meeting%20the%20above%20criteria%20included%201%2C974%20investors%2C%20a%205%25%20increase%20from%20last%20year's.%20Women%20comprised%2011%25%20of%20all%20seed%20investors%20in%20scope%2C%20up%208%25%20from%20the%20release%20of%20the%20first%20Seed%20100%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20final%20list%20included%2022%20investors%20who%20increased%20their%20rank%2C%2030%20with%20the%20same%20or%20lower%20rank%2C%20and%2048%20new%20investors.%20Twenty-seven%20investors%20in%20this%20year's%20ranking%20were%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-25-best-female-early-stage-investors-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2021%20Seed%20100%20list%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f64fc89-4514-47aa-b141-a40aad8d32df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20improved%20model%20of%20investment%20activity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20models%20have%20always%20factored%20in%20how%20active%20investors%20are%2C%20with%20investors%20estimated%20to%20do%20little%20to%20no%20investing%20ranked%20lower.%20However%2C%20investment%20activity%20has%20fluctuated%20over%20the%20years.%20While%20seed%20investment%20coverage%20across%20major%20data%20providers%20is%20spotty%2C%20we%20can%20still%20obtain%20trend%20estimates%20by%20analyzing%20aggregate%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20we%20show%20the%20total%20number%20of%20seed%20investments%20divided%20by%20the%20number%20of%20active%20seed%20investors%20in%20the%20US%20from%202010%20to%20the%20present.%20This%20is%20based%20on%20the%20set%20of%20investors%20that%20are%20input%20into%20our%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20models.%20The%20total%20count%20fluctuates%20a%20lot%2C%20by%20up%20to%2050%25%20over%20the%20timeframe%20of%20the%20Seed%20100%20series%2C%20and%20by%20more%20over%20a%20longer%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221247%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Termina%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a075245ecd7cc1332bb02a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnnual%20seed%20investments%20per%20active%20investor%3Cp%3ETermina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ECrunchbase%20and%20Termina%20analysis.%20Active%20investors%20are%20seed%20investors%20who%20have%20made%20a%20recent%20investment%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20changed%20this%20indicator%20to%20act%20more%20predominantly%20as%20a%20simple%20gate%20to%20remove%20investors%20who%20were%20clearly%20inactive.%20The%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20aim%20to%20help%20the%20ecosystem%20navigate%2C%20find%2C%20and%20celebrate%20great%20seed%20investors.%20Our%20updated%20activity%20logic%20is%20more%20inclusive%20across%20investment%20strategies%2C%20while%20still%20emphasizing%20investors%20still%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20plan%20to%20improve%20the%20model%20in%20the%20future%20by%20including%20a%20new%20counter-consensus%20indicator%20around%20sector%20selection.%20Some%20may%20view%20sector%20selection%20as%20one%20of%20the%20important%20insights%20of%20a%20great%20seed%20investor%20%E2%80%94%20the%20visionary%20investors%20of%20the%20past%2010%20years%20had%20big%20AI%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20future%20holds%20is%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20want%20the%20ranking%20to%20overemphasize%20recent%20success%20given%20current%20market%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJake%20Ellowitz%20is%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20a