3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGetting%20carded%20at%20a%20bar%20is%20sometimes%20taken%20as%20a%20compliment%20to%20one's%20youthful%20appearance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20Waymo%20riders%20are%20getting%20age-checked%20and%20also%20taking%20it%20as%20a%20form%20of%20flattery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20robotaxi%20company%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20underage%20riders%20violating%20its%20terms%20of%20service.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20carded%20by%20a%20server%20is%20a%20classic%20form%20of%20flattery%20%E2%80%94%20an%20unintended%20way%20to%20let%20someone%20know%20they%20look%20younger%20than%20they%20are%20or%20just%20have%20a%20really%20effective%20skincare%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202026%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20getting%20age-checked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20Waymo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Waymo%20riders%20have%20reported%20receiving%20calls%20from%20a%20remote%20support%20agent%20during%20their%20trips%2C%20asking%20whether%20they're%20old%20enough%20to%20ride%20in%20the%20robotaxi.%20Some%20have%20posted%20their%20interactions%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20received%20a%20notification%20that%20there%20is%20a%20minor%20riding%20in%20the%20vehicle.%20Can%20I%20confirm%2C%20'How%20old%20are%20you%3F'%26quot%3B%20a%20support%20agent%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20one%20TikTok%20video.%20The%20rider%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%2031!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20bars%20people%20under%2018%20from%20riding%20its%20robotaxis%20without%20adult%20supervision.%20In%20Phoenix%2C%20the%20company%20offers%20teen%20accounts%20for%2014%20to%2017-year-olds.%20That%20hasn't%20stopped%20some%20parents%20from%20putting%20their%20underage%20kids%20inside%20a%20Waymo%2C%20using%20robotaxis%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxis-for-children-parenting-personal-chaffeur-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20chauffeurs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20crack%20down%20on%20violations%2C%20Waymo%20uses%20its%20in-cabin%20cameras%20to%20flag%20riders%20who%20could%20be%20breaking%20the%20rules.%20The%20company%20said%20on%20its%20website%20that%20it%20also%20uses%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20models%2C%20but%20said%20that%20it%20does%20not%20use%20facial%20recognition%20or%20biometric%20identification%20to%20identify%20the%20riders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225028%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%20cabin%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a092aa694eb4c909fb2d438%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223771%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo%20said%20it%20has%20interior%20cameras%20for%20safety%2C%20security%2C%20and%20maintenance.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20not%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiders%20who%20say%20they%20are%20well%20over%2018%20have%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20their%20curious%20experience%20of%20being%20carded%20by%20a%20Waymo.%20Some%20can't%20tell%20if%20it's%20a%20backhanded%20compliment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20%40Waymo%20age%20verification%20call%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20my%20ride%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Seema%20Amble%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20the%20new%20version%20of%20getting%20carded%3F%20Should%20I%20be%20flattered%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20social%20media%20user%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20handle%20%40clarahyee%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity%20to%20share%20her%20skincare%20routine%20with%20her%20followers%20after%20she%20was%20carded%20by%20a%20Waymo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere's%20the%20skincare%20routine%20that%20made%20Waymo%20AND%20Uber%20think%20I'm%20a%20minor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWaymo%20operator%20just%20interrupted%20my%20trip%20on%20rider%20support%20to%20verify%20that%20I%20was%20over%2018.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHonestly%E2%80%A6.%20Thank%20you%3F!%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Christina%20Melas-Kyriazi%20(%40ChristinaPhili5)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChristinaPhili5%2Fstatus%2F2055329940405674234%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2015%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo's%20age-verification%20process%20may%20have%20also%20flagged%20edge-case%20riders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanh%20Trang%2C%20a%20South%20Park%20Commons%20partner%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20he%20has%20achondroplasia%20%E2%80%94%20a%20genetic%20condition%20that%20affects%20bone%20growth%20and%20is%20the%20most%20common%20form%20of%20dwarfism.%20About%201%20in%2015%2C000%20to%201%20in%2040%2C000%20people%20are%20born%20with%20the%20condition%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Cleveland%20Clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Waymo%20flagged%20his%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%2039.%20I%20have%20achondroplasia.%20I'm%204'2%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3B%20Trang%20said.%20%26quot%3B%40Waymo%2C%20hope%20this%20makes%20it%20into%20a%20future%20model%20update.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrang%20added%20to%20his%20X%20post%20that%20this%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20typical%20achondroplasia%20experience%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20mostly%20shared%20it%20because%20he%20%26quot%3Bthought%20it%20was%20funny.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20of%20carding%20moments%20shared%20online%20show%20that%20the%20verification%20process%20typically%20involves%20a%20rider%20support%20agent%20asking%20the%20rider%20for%20their%20age%20and%20confirming%20they're%20the%20account%20holder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Waymo%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20will%20continue%20to%20refine%20its%20system%20and%20processes%20for%20accuracy%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20riders%2C%20we%20have%20policies%20in%20place%20to%20help%20us%20identify%20violations%20of%20our%20terms%20of%20service%2C%20including%20age%20eligibility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20times%2C%20we%20may%20contact%20riders%20to%20verify%20they%20are%20aged%2018%20years%20or%20older%20%E2%80%94%20or%2014-17%20for%20authorized%20teen%20accounts%20in%20Phoenix.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutonomous%20cars%20like%20Waymo%20haven't%20taken%20over%20the%20world%2C%20but%20they're%20already%20showing%20how%20frontier%20technology%20adds%20new%20quirks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20to%20modern%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20camera%20attached%20to%20a%20Waymo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a09292894eb4c909fb2d434%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo's%20fifth-generation%20platform%20has%20nearly%2030%20cameras%20attached%20to%20the%20vehicle.%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Tamargo%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Waymo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20San%20Francisco%2C%20a%20robotaxi%20hub%2C%20riders%20might%20use%20Waymo%20like%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjared-friedman-y-combinator-wamo-office-on-wheels-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoffice%20on%20wheels%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20women%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-woman-gave-birth-san-francisco-robotaxi-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egiven%20birth%20inside%20of%20Waymos%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-doordash-pay-drivers-shut-robotaxi-doors-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C