et%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Pizza%20Hut%20franchisee%20alleged%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20chain's%20AI%20system%20damaged%20its%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20suit%20alleges%20that%20the%20system%20led%20to%20delays%20and%20cratering%20sales%20at%20over%20100%20restaurants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20franchisee%2C%20Chaac%20Pizza%20Northeast%2C%20is%20seeking%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20top%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Franking-restaurant-reset-winners-losers-red-lobster-cracker-barrel-starbucks-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPizza%20Hut%3C%2Fa%3E%20franchisee%20says%20the%20chain's%20rollout%20of%20an%20AI-powered%20delivery%20system%20turned%20once-speedy%20pizza%20orders%20into%20a%20cold%2C%20late-arriving%20mess%20%E2%80%94%20and%20cratered%20a%20business%20that%20had%20been%20outperforming%20nearly%20every%20other%20operator%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20on%20May%206%20in%20Texas%20Business%20Court%2C%20franchisee%20Chaac%20Pizza%20Northeast%20accused%20Pizza%20Hut%20of%20forcing%20stores%20to%20adopt%20Dragontail%2C%20a%20delivery-management%20platform%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20Pizza%20Hut%20described%20as%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20%26quot%3Boptimize%26quot%3B%20food%20delivery%2C%20despite%20what%20the%20suit%20calls%20obvious%20incompatibilities%20with%20Chaac's%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaac%2C%20which%20operates%20about%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E111%20Pizza%20Hut%20restaurants%20across%20New%20York%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Maryland%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%2C%20alleges%20the%20system%20caused%20%26quot%3Bcascading%20operational%20breakdowns%20and%20customer%20dissatisfaction%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20gave%20DoorDash%20drivers%20real-time%20visibility%20into%20kitchen%20workflows%20and%20order%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20franchisee%20says%20the%20fallout%20exceeded%20%24100%20million%20in%20lost%20business%20and%20enterprise%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Dragontail's%20rollout%2C%20Chaac%20says%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20its%20pizza%20deliveries%20arrived%20within%2030%20minutes%2C%20and%20the%20company%20consistently%20posted%20double-digit%20sales%20growth%20and%20guest-satisfaction%20scores%20above%20system%20averages.%20After%20Pizza%20Hut%20rolled%20out%20Dragontail%20in%202024%2C%20the%20franchisee%20says%20delivery%20performance%20sharply%20deteriorated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-plans-to-spend-100-million-on-driver-gas-benefits-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDoorDash%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20waiting%20to%20batch%20multiple%20orders%20together%20after%20gaining%20virtual%20visibility%20into%20kitchen%20systems%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20see%20when%20pizzas%20would%20come%20out%20of%20the%20oven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20immediately%20leaving%20with%20a%20completed%20order%2C%20the%20suit%20claims%20drivers%20waited%20%26quot%3Bup%20to%20fifteen%20(15)%20minutes%26quot%3B%20for%20additional%20deliveries%2C%20increasing%20the%20time%20between%20when%20a%20pizza%20is%20removed%20from%20the%20oven%20rack%20and%20when%20it%20leaves%20the%20building%20to%20be%20delivered.%20That%20delay%20slowed%20deliveries%2C%20disappointed%20customers%2C%20and%20caused%20a%20sharp%20drop%20in%20sales%2C%20the%20suit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20also%20alleges%20Dashers%20could%20see%20tip%20amounts%20and%20whether%20orders%20were%20cash%20payments%2C%20making%20some%20drivers%20less%20likely%20to%20accept%20certain%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20intention%20to%20improve%20efficiency%20and%20service%20to%20the%20customer%2C%20Dragontail%20did%20the%20exact%20opposite%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20caused%20significant%20delays%20and%20pummeled%20consumer%20satisfaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaac%20alleges%20Pizza%20Hut%20failed%20to%20adequately%20train%20operators%20on%20the%20system%2C%20refused%20requests%20for%20support%2C%20and%20ignored%20worsening%20delivery%20metrics%20after%20sales%20began%20plunging%20in%20key%20markets.%20In%20New%20York%20City%2C%20the%20franchisee%20says%20year-over-year%20sales%20growth%20swung%20from%20positive%2010.19%25%20to%20negative%209.78%25%20after%20the%20rollout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20argues%20Pizza%20Hut%20breached%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-passive-income-through-franchise-investing-strategy-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efranchise%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20mandating%20continued%20use%20of%20the%20software%20while%20failing%20to%20exercise%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20business%20judgment%26quot%3B%20or%20modify%20the%20system%20to%20accommodate%20Chaac's%20reliance%20on%20DoorDash%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaac%20is%20seeking%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20in%20damages%2C%20plus%20attorneys'%20fees%20and%20other%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20emailed%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20Pizza%20Hut%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20was%20reviewing%20the%20lawsuit's%20claims%20and%20would%20respond%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20the%20appropriate%20legal%20channels%E2%80%9D%20but%20declined%20to%20comment%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20DoorDash%20and%20attorneys%20for%20Chaac%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20lands%20as%20Pizza%20Hut%20faces%20broader%20pressure%20across%20its%20US%20business.%20The%20chain's%20parent%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-pizza-hut-struggling-value-proposition-yum-brands-explores-sale-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYum!%20Brands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20last%20year%20it%20was%20exploring%20strategic%20options%20for%20the%20struggling%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20possible%20sale%20%E2%80%94%20after%20Pizza%20Hut%20posted%20multiple%20consecutive%20quarters%20of%20declining%20same-store%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20February%20earnings%20call%2C%20Yum!%20Brands%20announced%20plans%20to%20shutter%20250%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurant-chains-closing-locations-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPizza%20Hut%20locations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20have%20said%20the%20brand%20has%20struggled%20to%20compete%20in%20an%20increasingly%20crowded%20market%2C%20where%20rivals%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdominos-cmo-rebrand-new-logo-jingle-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDomino's%20Pizza%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Little%20Caesars%20have%20leaned%20heavily%20into%20low-cost%20deals%20and%20delivery%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpizza-hut-ai-system-dragontail-lawsuit-franchisee-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779091861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a08f9ed94eb4c909fb2d40c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpizza-hut-ai-system-dragontail-lawsuit-franchisee-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pizza%20Hut's%20AI-powered%20Dragontail%20system%20led%20to%20%24100M%20in%20lost%20business%2C%20a%20franchisee%20says%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20over%20delivery%20delays.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%2C%20Nigeria%20launch%20fresh%20kinetic%20strikes%20on%20ISIS%20targets%22%2