20LAXMI%2C%20KHUSHI%20BHUTA%2C%20AJAY%20TOMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20are%20the%203%20drones%20Ukraine%20used%20to%20pierce%20Moscow's%20air%20defense%20gauntlet%20in%20its%20biggest%20attack%20yet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20angles%20of%20smoke%20billowing%20from%20an%20oil%20facility%20in%20Moscow%20that%20came%20under%20attack.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a9351abc4e9d88574ae7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20said%20it%20had%20struck%20multiple%20targets%20in%20Moscow%2C%20including%20an%20oil%20pumping%20station%2C%20with%20its%20long-range%20drones.%3Cp%3ETelegram%2FUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20launched%20its%20largest%20drone%20attack%20on%20Moscow%20yet%2C%20saying%20it%20used%20locally%20made%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20it%20hit%20targets%20including%20a%20microchip%20facility%20and%20an%20oil%20pumping%20station%20in%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20mentioned%20three%20types%20of%20long-range%20drones%2C%20including%20one%20previously%20unknown%20variant.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20it%20used%20three%20types%20of%20locally%20produced%20drones%20to%20pummel%20the%20Moscow%20region%2C%20in%20its%20biggest%20attack%20so%20far%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoscow-bans-almost-everyone-from-posting-about-drone-strikes-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavily%20defended%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20General%20Staff%20of%20Ukraine's%20Armed%20Forces%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%20that%20it%20used%20the%20FP-1%20Firepoint%20and%20RS-1%20Bars%20winged%20drones%20to%20hit%20several%20targets%20in%20the%20Moscow%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20previously%20unknown%20third%20type%20of%20drone%2C%20called%20the%20Bars-SM%20Gladiator%2C%20was%20also%20used%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20May%2016%20and%20during%20the%20night%20of%20May%2017%2C%202026%2C%20units%20of%20Ukraine's%20Defense%20Forces%20struck%20a%20number%20of%20key%20Russian%20military%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20increasingly%20sought%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20these%20drones%2C%20newly%20developed%20and%20relatively%20cheap%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20long-range%20weapons%2C%20by%20ramping%20up%20strikes%20deep%20into%20Russian%20territory%20and%20against%20Moscow.%20The%20capital%20is%20home%20to%20Russia's%20densest%20air%20defense%20network%20by%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%20were%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20Ukrainian%20barrage%20across%20the%20country%20this%20weekend%20that%20Russian%20authorities%20said%20killed%20at%20least%20four%20people%2C%20including%20three%20in%20the%20Moscow%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Moscow%20alone%2C%20the%20local%20mayor%2C%20Sergei%20Sobyanin%2C%20said%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20attack%26quot%3B%20involved%20over%20120%20drones%2C%20the%20highest%20number%20ever%20reported%20in%20the%20urban%20region%20for%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224983%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smashed-in%20windows%20and%20balconies%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20this%20building%20in%20Moscow.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a9447abc4e9d88574ae80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223322%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocal%20residents%20inspect%20a%20damaged%20balcony%20in%20a%20residential%20building%20following%20an%20air%20attack%20in%20Krasnogorsk%2C%20Moscow%20region.%3Cp%3ETATYANA%20MAKEYEVA%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20General%20Staff%20said%20that%20among%20the%20targets%20hit%20were%20a%20microchip%20facility%20about%2018%20miles%20from%20central%20Moscow%20and%20a%20major%20oil%20pumping%20station%20about%2030%20miles%20from%20central%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad01d0c1-31ed-4f5d-a780-ee08f29fb8bc%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20homegrown%20arsenal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flack-western-weapons-pushed-ukraine-make-gear-west-now-wants-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethree%20Ukrainian%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%2C%20the%20least%20is%20publicly%20known%20about%20the%20Bars-SM%20Gladiator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20General%20Staff%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20and%20its%20defense%20ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider%20about%20this%20weekend's%20attacks%20or%20the%20three%20drone%20types.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20its%20name%20could%20indicate%20the%20Gladiator%20related%20to%20the%20RS-1%20Bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20drone%20was%20unveiled%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202025%20as%20a%20mix%20between%20a%20cruise%20missile%20and%20a%20jet-powered%20uncrewed%20aerial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20RS-1%20Bars%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20mass-produced%20while%20being%20able%20to%20hit%20targets%20up%20to%20500%20miles%20away%20with%20about%20100%20to%20200%20pounds%20of%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20hasn't%20revealed%20who%20makes%20the%20RS-1%20Bars%2C%20though%20it%20has%20said%20that%20the%20winged%20drone%20was%20developed%20by%20private%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20more%20has%20been%20publicly%20disclosed%20about%20the%20FP-1%20Firepoint%2C%20a%20fixed-wing%20drone%20produced%20in%20late%202024%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-drones-hit-deep-in-russia-security-source-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeep-strike%20missions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%20900%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20long-range%20fixed%20wing%20drone%20sits%20on%20a%20factory%20production%20floor.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a93b894eb4c909fb2d5d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFire%20Point%20builds%20two%20long-range%20drones%2C%20the%20FP-1%20and%20FP-2.%20It%20also%20builds%20a%20long-range%20missile%20called%20the%20Flamingo%2C%20which%20Ukraine%20has%20touted%20as%20one%20of%20its%20main%20weapons%20for%20deep%20strikes%20into%20Russia.%3Cp%3ESerhii%20Okunev%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShaped%20like%20a%20small%20plane%2C%20the%20FP-1%20is%20designed%20by%20its%20namesake%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-cant-afford-weapons-purchases-partner-gives-way-increase-production-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elocal%20firm%20Fire%20Point%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20carry%20up%20to%20roughly%20260%20pounds%20of%20explosives.%20The%20turbojet%20drone%20is%20made%20to%20be%20launched%20easily%20without%20a%20runway%2C%20taking%20off%20with%20a%20rocket%20booster%20from%20a%20rail%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20BBC%20reported%20that%20Fire%20Point%20makes%20its%20drones%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20%2450%2C000%20each%20and%20is%20producing%20at%20least%20200%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20RS-1%20Bars%2C%20it%20straddles%20the%20line%20between%20cruise%20missile%20and%20drone%2C%20though%20these%20one-way%20munitions%20travel%20much%20more%20slowly%20than%20a%20conventional%20cruise%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20declared%20range%20of%20both%20drones%20is%20well%20beyond%20the%20distance%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20Moscow%2C%20which%20is%20about%20300%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9ae0e08-a29b-4e04-b8fd-3d8ecf3e1936%5C%22%3ECracking%20Moscow's%20defenses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStriking%20Moscow%20would%20require%20a%20drone%20to%20penetrate%20a%20multilayered%20air%20defense%20system%2C%20which%20includes%20two%20rings%20of%20S-300%20and%20S-400%20long-range%20surface-to-air%20missile%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20capital%20also%20fields%20an%20assortment%20of%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%20and%20dozens%20of%20point-defense%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Pantsir%20and%20Tor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Kremlin%20geared%20up%20for%20its%20high-profile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-victory-day-photos-show-small-event-key-weapons-missing-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVictory%20Day%20parade%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20open-source%20intelligence%20analysts%20said%20satellite%20images%20showed%20over%20100%20such%20defenses%20spread%20across%20a%2070-mile%20radius%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concentration%20of%20Russian%20air%20defense%20systems%20in%20the%20Moscow%20region%20is%20the%20largest.%20But%20we%20are%20overcoming%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20popular%20Russian%20Telegram%20news%20channels%20have%20uploaded%20footage%20that%20appears%20to%20corroborate%20the%20General%20Staff's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20widely%20shared%20clip%20published%20by%20the%20channel%20ASTRA%20showed%20a%20major%20fire%20at%20the%20Elma%20Technopark%20in%20Zelenograd%2C%20a%20Moscow%20district%20home%20to%20the%20Angstrom%20semiconductor%20plant.%20The%20facility%20builds%20key%20electronics%20for%20precision-guided%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20clip%20also%20shows%20a%20massive%20fire%20at%20the%20Solnechnogorskaya%20pumping%20station%2C%20which%20was%20later%20extinguished%20by%20emergency%20crews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20channels%20have%20also%20reported%20fires%20near%20Moscow's%20air%20travel%20hub%2C%20Sheremetyevo%20International%20Airport%2C%20and%20posted%20clips%20of%20winged%20drones%20flying%20over%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20firefighter%20covered%20in%20foam%20walks%20past%20a%20burned%20fence%20underneath%20an%20overpass.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a949694eb4c909fb2d5d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmergency%20services%20responded%20after%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20under%20an%20overpass%20in%20Moscow%20on%20Sunday.%3Cp%3EYulia%20Morozova%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Zelenskyy%20said%20his%20country%20had%20also%20carried%20out%20strikes%20across%20Russia%20and%20occupied%20Ukrainian%20territories%2C%20including%20Crimea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20attack%20came%20several%20days%20after%20Russia%20launched%20one%20of%20its%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-daytime-drone-attack-nighttime-missile-barrage-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintense%20and%20longest%20drone%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20war%20so%20far%2C%20sending%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-daytime-drone-strikes-night-shahed-ukraine-war-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E1%2C500%20drones%20at%20Ukrainian%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20span%20of%20two%20days.%20Zelenskyy%20said%20his%20country%20would%20respond%20in%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20defense%20ministry%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20it%20had%20shot%20down%201%2C054%20Ukrainian%20fixed-wing%20drones%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-long-range-moscow-air-defenses-biggest-attack-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779087035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.c