17e6e1443b8dc48e42cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223730%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20next%20AI%20investment%20wave%20could%20emerge%20in%20liquid%20cooling%20systems%20for%20data%20centers.%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20now%20see%20AI%20stocks%20as%20a%20defensive%20trade%20amid%20macro%20fears%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Shawn%20Tuteja%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20see%20AI%20demand%20as%20more%20%26quot%3Binelastic%26quot%3B%20amid%20inflation%20fears%20and%20slowing%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWall%20Street's%20next%20AI%20trade%20could%20be%20liquid%20cooling%20systems%20for%20power-hungry%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20ongoing%20questions%20about%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackrock-larry-fink-ai-bubble-china-competition-davos-wef-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20in%20a%20bubble%2C%20Wall%20Street%20is%20now%20treating%20AI%20more%20like%20a%20defensive%20trade%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20returning%20to%20AI%20stocks%20as%20inflation%20fears%2C%20elevated%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20slowing%20economic%20growth%20darken%20the%20outlook%20for%20the%20broader%20economy%2C%20said%20Shawn%20Tuteja%2C%20who%20oversees%20ETF%20and%20custom%20baskets%20volatility%20trading%20within%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20global%20banking%20and%20markets%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20this%20massive%20rotation%20back%20into%20the%20hyperscalers%2C%20back%20into%20the%20AI%20names%20as%20people%20view%20that%20story%20as%20more%20inelastic%20demand%20and%20able%20to%20withstand%20the%20things%20that%20the%20consumers%20aren't%2C%26quot%3B%20Tuteja%20said%20on%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20%26quot%3BThe%20Markets%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20marks%20a%20sharp%20reversal%20from%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20when%20investors%20expected%20falling%20inflation%2C%20Federal%20Reserve%20rate%20cuts%2C%20and%20stronger%20cyclical%20growth%20to%20drive%20gains%20in%20sectors%20like%20homebuilders%2C%20industrials%2C%20and%20consumer%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20persistent%20inflation%20and%20geopolitical%20tensions%20have%20pushed%20investors%20back%20toward%20AI-linked%20companies%2C%20which%20many%20now%20see%20as%20more%20insulated%20from%20economic%20weakness%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fnasdaq_100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Nasdaq%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20up%20about%2026%25%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsox-semiconductor-index-historic-rally-ai-nvidia-tsmc-mu-avgo-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPhiladelphia%20Semiconductor%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20up%20over%2060%25%20off%20their%20March%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuteja%20said%20the%20rally%20is%20still%20being%20driven%20by%20real%20spending%20rather%20than%20pure%20speculation%2C%20pointing%20to%20hyperscalers%20committing%20to%20spend%20roughly%20%24755%20billion%20in%20capital%20expenditures%20this%20year%2C%20up%2038%25%20year%20over%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20the%20semiconductor%20earnings%20are%20always%20beating%2C%20because%20there's%20just%20so%20much%20capex%20going%20into%20the%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df0ad74c-85ec-4e68-bbaf-08878f2c075d%5C%22%3EThe%20next%20big%20AI%20trade%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spending%20boom%20is%20also%20pushing%20investors%20to%20search%20for%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20trade%20beyond%20semiconductors%2C%20data%20centers%2C%20memory%20chips%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptics-stocks-memory-chips-ai-trade-lite-cien-glw-cohr-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoptical%20tech.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20baskets%20team%20sees%20the%20next%20spin-off%20or%20the%20next%20iteration%20of%20the%20AI%20equipment%20trade%20being%20within%20liquid%20cooling%2C%26quot%3B%20Tuteja%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20systems%20that%20could%20sharply%20reduce%20the%20massive%20energy%20demands%20required%20to%20cool%20traditional%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20optimism%20surrounding%20AI%2C%20Tuteja%20warned%20that%20investors%20may%20be%20underestimating%20how%20volatile%20the%20trade%20could%20become%2C%20as%20leveraged%20products%20tied%20to%20semiconductors%20could%20amplify%20market%20swings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20don't%20just%20go%20up%20all%20the%20time.%20They%20can%20also%20have%20violent%20corrections.%20And%20we%20haven't%20really%20seen%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20the%20AI%20trade%20is%20in%20a%20bubble%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20does%20mean%20that%20there%20could%20be%20some%20two-way%20volatility%20in%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-ai-defensive-trade-next-big-winner-cooling-systems-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779082650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a7f8e94eb4c909fb2d5b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-ai-defensive-trade-next-big-winner-cooling-systems-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20little-watched%20part%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20market%20could%20power%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20AI%20boom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2