%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mike%20Tyson%20says%20one%20self-talk%20lesson%20he%20learned%20as%20a%20kid%20shaped%20his%20boxing%20career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222789%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Tyson%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a79a894eb4c909fb2d5a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike%20Tyson%20says%20his%20mentor%2C%20Cus%20D'amato%2C%20taught%20him%20a%20lesson%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20self-talk.%3Cp%3EAl%20Bello%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Netflix%20%C2%A9%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMike%20Tyson%2C%2059%2C%20says%20his%20mentor%2C%20Cus%20D'Amato%2C%20taught%20him%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20positive%20self-talk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20learn%20that%20at%2012%20to%20be%20the%20champion%20at%2020%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20world%20heavyweight%20boxing%20champion%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeyond%20the%20ring%2C%20Tyson%20said%20D'Amato%20gave%20him%20a%20sense%20of%20support%20and%20stability%20in%20his%20personal%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-tyson-net-worth-career-earnings-money-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMike%20Tyson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2059%2C%20says%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%20from%20his%20mentor%2C%20Cus%20D'Amato%2C%20helped%20shape%20the%20mindset%20that%20made%20him%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-floyd-mayweathers-post-boxing-investments-career-debt-real-estate-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboxing%20champion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20had%20my%20mentor%2C%20he%20told%20me%20not%20to%20ever%20say%20anything%20negative%20about%20myself.%20But%20to%20say%20beautiful%20things%20about%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyson%20told%20host%20Theo%20Von%20on%20Friday's%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLkWU9lB2zEQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThis%20Past%20Weekend%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyson%20said%20his%20mentor%20believed%20that%20the%20mind%20doesn't%20distinguish%20between%20jokes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkylie-kelce-models-positive-self-talk-daughters-parenting-confidence-motherhood-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenuine%20self-criticism%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways%20say%20beautiful%20things%20about%20myself%20and%20never%20say%20anything%20negative%20about%20myself%20because%20my%20subconscious%20don't%20know%20if%20I'm%20playing%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20learning%20that%20lesson%20early%20in%20life%20paid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20learn%20that%20at%2012%20to%20be%20the%20champion%20at%2020.%20You%20know%2C%20if%20I%20learned%20it%20at%2015%2C%2016%2C%20hey%2C%20it%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20worked%20out.%20Then%20I'd%20have%20been%20champion%2022%20probably%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20everything%20worked%20out%20for%20the%20right%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyson%20first%20started%20boxing%20while%20at%20a%20reform%20school%20in%20New%20York%2C%20where%20he%20was%20introduced%20to%20D'Amato%2C%20a%20boxing%20coach%20and%20promoter%2C%20by%20former%20boxer%20Bobby%20Stewart%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20school%20as%20a%20counselor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Tyson's%20mother%20died%2C%20D'Amato%20became%20his%20legal%20guardian%20and%20continued%20training%20him%20until%20his%20own%20death%20in%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201986%2C%20Tyson%20became%20the%20youngest%20world%20heavyweight%20boxing%20champion%20at%2020%20years%2C%20145%20days%20old.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20finish%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dcddaa1fe10f45375e1ed71c479d58a72cd5b57dbfe2e115a791d91f4987fd2e6%26postID%3D6a0a727dea9599c045f469e5%26postSlug%3Dmike-tyson-positive-self-talk-advice-boxing-champion-2026-5%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fboxing%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F39717002%252Fmike-tyson-biography-boxing-record-fights-more%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%2050%20wins%2C%20including%2044%20knockouts%2C%20before%20retiring%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20boxing%2C%20Tyson%20said%20D'Amato%20also%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20his%20personal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20memories%20he%20wished%20had%20been%20captured%20on%20camera%2C%20Tyson%20immediately%20pointed%20to%20the%20time%20he%20first%20met%20his%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20part%20I%20wish%20could%20come%20back.%20I%20miss%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20why%20the%20period%20still%20meant%20so%20much%20to%20him%2C%20he%20said%20D'Amato%20made%20him%20feel%20cared%20for%20and%20supported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20somebody%20I%20loved%2C%20and%20they%20loved%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20with%20D'Amato%20also%20gave%20him%20structure%20and%20taught%20him%20discipline%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20Tyson%20said%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20improve%20his%20grades%2C%20do%20chores%20around%20the%20house%2C%20and%20clean%20the%20gym%20after%20training%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20like%20my%20father.%20He%20was%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-my-daughters-to-a-prison-to-visit-their-father-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadopted%20father%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20my%20legally%20adopted%20father.%20I%20wasn't%20out%20of%20his%20sight%20much.%20He%20didn't%20let%20me%20out%20of%20his%20sight%20much.%20He%20watched%20who%20I%20hung%20out%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyson%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20my%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyson%20isn't%20th